# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:19
translate jp a1_sunday_dont_panic_1310289a:

    # "The next day, I wake up feeling a little lightheaded. It's almost noon already."
    "翌日。頭がくらくらするのを感じながら目を覚ます。もう正午近い。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:23
translate jp a1_sunday_dont_panic_1791ed4f:

    # "Sleeping late is fine, since it's a Sunday and there are no classes."
    "朝寝坊しても問題はない。今日は日曜で授業はないのだから。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:25
translate jp a1_sunday_dont_panic_d1dd5936:

    # "Not just a Sunday, though, but the festival as well."
    "とはいえ今日は、ただの日曜じゃなくて学園祭の日でもある。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:27
translate jp a1_sunday_dont_panic_007b9c25:

    # "From my window I can already see some people at the soba booth slinging noodles onto plates for people with a craving for low-quality food."
    "窓の外には、もうそばの屋台に人がいるのが見える。ジャンクフードに目がない人たちのために、麺をお皿に乱暴に盛りつけている。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:29
translate jp a1_sunday_dont_panic_4737fe4f:

    # "I throw back a handful of my morning meds and ponder how to spend the day."
    "一握り分の朝の薬を一気に飲みこみ、今日一日どう過ごそうかと考える。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:31
translate jp a1_sunday_dont_panic_8c9aadb4:

    # "There will be a few exams in the coming week, but I don't consider those as ominous as others, so I'm not as worried about them as I probably should be."
    "来週には試験があるけど、みんなが言うほど忌々しくは思わない。多分、本当はもっと心配してなきゃいけないんだろうな。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:33
translate jp a1_sunday_dont_panic_ba9c4ec9:

    # "With no urgent obligations regarding education, I should be free to spend the day at the festival as I like."
    "まあすぐに勉強しないといけないわけでもないし、この学園祭の日にどう過ごしたって自由なはずだ。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:38
translate jp a1_sunday_dont_panic_cca8f25f:

    # "Finishing my morning routine, I exit into the hallway, intending to go out and find something to eat."
    "朝の雑用を済ませ、廊下へと出る。外で何か食べるものを探そう。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:40
translate jp a1_sunday_dont_panic_70f5829a:

    # "Passing by his door, I decide to see what Kenji's up to today out of impulse."
    "健二の部屋の前を通りすぎようとした時ふと思いつき、あいつが今日どうするのか聞いてみることにする。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:42
translate jp a1_sunday_dont_panic_7b43c6e4:

    # "I'm curious if he has any plans, since everyone is doing something."
    "あいつに予定があるのか気になる。みんな何かしらやってるし。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:44
translate jp a1_sunday_dont_panic_89afc92d:

    # "Then again, I can picture him having built a soundproof shelter in his room."
    "と言いながらも、自室に防音シェルターなんかを作り終えているあいつの姿もありありと想像できる。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:46
translate jp a1_sunday_dont_panic_c92ebf01:

    # "Or possibly something like a fort, complete with 'No Girls Allowed' sign."
    "あるいは要塞みたいなものとか。もちろん『女子立ち入り禁止』と掲げてあるやつ。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:48
translate jp a1_sunday_dont_panic_00886374:

    # "… and with the 'Girls' crossed out and 'body' crudely scrawled underneath it."
    "……そして『女子』が横線で消され、その下に『何人たりとも』と乱暴に書き直されてるんだ。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:54
translate jp a1_sunday_dont_panic_850979b5:

    # "Knocking on his door which is luckily devoid of any kind of sign, I hear again the unsettling clicking of at least ten locks being pulled back. The door opens up a crack."
    "健二の部屋のドアを叩く。幸い、何の注意書きも掲げられてはいなかった。 また落ち着かないカチャカチャという鍵の音が聞こえてくる──少なくとも１０個はあるようだ。ドアがバタンと開く。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:64
translate jp a1_sunday_dont_panic_63e10f06:

    # ke "Who is it?"
    ke "誰だ？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:66
translate jp a1_sunday_dont_panic_59c0e773:

    # hi "You're supposed to ask that before you open the door."
    hi "それは開ける前に聞くもんだろ"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:74
translate jp a1_sunday_dont_panic_beb9e517:

    # ke "Oh, it's you. Damn, it's early."
    ke "ああ、久夫か。くそ、朝早いな"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:76
translate jp a1_sunday_dont_panic_b85a6543:

    # hi "It's not really that early."
    hi "いや特に早くないと思うけど"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:81
translate jp a1_sunday_dont_panic_3a944c85:

    # ke "What is it, man?"
    ke "なんの用だ？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:83
translate jp a1_sunday_dont_panic_733efe97:

    # hi "Nothing, was just gonna ask what you're gonna do today."
    hi "特に。ただ今日どうするのか聞きたくて"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:85
translate jp a1_sunday_dont_panic_8634de2e:

    # hi "Half the school is out there already."
    hi "もう生徒はみんな外に出てるぞ"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:90
translate jp a1_sunday_dont_panic_10b94152:

    # ke "Out where? Why?"
    ke "外のどこだよ？　どうして？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:92
translate jp a1_sunday_dont_panic_81d99227:

    # hi "What?"
    hi "なんだよ？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:94
translate jp a1_sunday_dont_panic_dc70de62:

    # ke "What what? Is today special? Why are they there? Who are?"
    ke "なにってなんだ？　今日って特別な日か？　なんでそんな所に。どんなやつらが？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:99
translate jp a1_sunday_dont_panic_0a8c993e:

    # ke "I can hear them. It's loud… don't tell me… Has the invasion begun?"
    ke "いや、聞こえるぞ。騒がしいな……まさか……侵略が始まったっていうのか？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:101
translate jp a1_sunday_dont_panic_c12af1fe:

    # "He suddenly looks more alarmed."
    "急に心配そうな顔をする健二。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:106
translate jp a1_sunday_dont_panic_7940a3d4:

    # ke "What day is it, man?"
    ke "今日って何曜日だ？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:108
translate jp a1_sunday_dont_panic_3d3c1c94:

    # hi "Yeah I guess you can't see the big wooden booths outside, and people selling stuff…"
    hi "ああ、お前にはあのでかい屋台の列も見えないんだろうな……売ってる人間も……"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:110
translate jp a1_sunday_dont_panic_f24bf65b:

    # ke "What the hell are you talking about? I have my curtains closed at all times to thwart the snipers."
    ke "いったい何の話だよ？　俺はスナイパー避けに、いつもカーテン閉めてるんだよ"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:112
translate jp a1_sunday_dont_panic_435498cb:

    # hi "Uhh, it's the festival. You know that… right?"
    hi "あー、学園祭だよ。知ってる……よな？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:117
translate jp a1_sunday_dont_panic_608da5f4:

    # ke "Oh shit, that's today? Ah, damn. Ah… damn. Dammit."
    ke "ああくそ、今日だったのか？　あー、くっそ。ああ……ちくしょう"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:119
translate jp a1_sunday_dont_panic_6d940e6d:

    # ke "I can't believe I forgot, I don't have my fort finished yet. This is bad."
    ke "忘れてたなんて信じられねえ、まだ要塞も完成してないのに。これはまずいぞ"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:121
translate jp a1_sunday_dont_panic_46afbfaa:

    # ke "This is going to be a very bad day… It's good you told me this, man. This is going to be a bad day."
    ke "今日は本当にひどい日になるぞ。お前、教えてくれてよかったぜ。今日は悪い日になる"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:123
translate jp a1_sunday_dont_panic_7df9d21b:

    # hi "Why?"
    hi "どうして？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:128
translate jp a1_sunday_dont_panic_b4a191bb:

    # ke "Oh man, they're going to be everywhere. The people. Outside my window. Socializing!"
    ke "おいおい、あいつらがあちこち歩き回るんだぞ。あいつらだよ。窓の外の。リア充してるやつら！"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:130
translate jp a1_sunday_dont_panic_9f539c65:

    # "Kenji rubs his temples nervously, suddenly looking very ill."
    "健二はこめかみをイラついたようにこする。急に顔色が悪くなった。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:135
translate jp a1_sunday_dont_panic_d1f8957f:

    # ke "It's going to be loud as hell. Damn, and I was going to go out today, but now it's ruined, everything is ruined."
    ke "ものすごく騒がしくなるぞ。くそ、今日は外に行くつもりだったのに、もう台無しだ。何もかも台無しだ"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:137
translate jp a1_sunday_dont_panic_35950027:

    # ke "This is awful. This sucks. This sucks!"
    ke "こんなのってあるかよ。ひでえ、ひどすぎる！"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:139
translate jp a1_sunday_dont_panic_b22f2172:

    # ke "What the hell, this really sucks. I can't go anywhere now. There's nowhere to run."
    ke "なんだこれ。本当にひどすぎるぞ。もうどこにも行けないじゃねえか。どこにも逃げられない"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:141
translate jp a1_sunday_dont_panic_7dc64d58:

    # "Kenji seems nervous. You could even say he's majorly freaking out."
    "気が立ってるようだ。気が狂ってると言ってもいいかも知れない。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:146
translate jp a1_sunday_dont_panic_edc6b507:

    # ke "I can't believe this. So that's what today was."
    ke "信じられない。今日がこの日だったのか"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:148
translate jp a1_sunday_dont_panic_8c147039:

    # ke "Damn, and I couldn't even prepare for it."
    ke "くそ、それなのに準備もできなかった"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:153
translate jp a1_sunday_dont_panic_a5dc7c42:

    # ke "I couldn't even brace myself and now it's here and I can't do anything. You should have told me this earlier, dude. I mean, at least, I know, but… I could have known earlier! Imagine what I could have accomplished…"
    ke "何の準備もできなくて、こんな事になっちまって、俺にはどうしようもないんだ。お前がもっと早く言ってくれれば良かったんだ というか、まあ、知ってるけど……もっと早くに気づくことだってできたはずだろ！　そしたらどれだけ準備できたか、考えてみろよ……"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:155
translate jp a1_sunday_dont_panic_51f888a1:

    # hi "Sorry. I thought you knew."
    hi "悪いな。知ってると思ってた"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:157
translate jp a1_sunday_dont_panic_b8aedbbb:

    # hi "So I guess you're not going to do anything today?"
    hi "つまり、お前今日は特に予定ないんだな？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:159
translate jp a1_sunday_dont_panic_26d2a047:

    # hi "The weather is even good. Yesterday was really windy, so I thought today would be cold. It's not, though, so there's no reason to just stay inside. Yeah, you should check the festival out."
    hi "天気は良いしさ。昨日は風が強かったから今日は寒くなるかと思ってたけど、そんなこともなかったし、部屋にこもってる理由なんてないだろ。お前も学園祭見に行くといい"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:161
translate jp a1_sunday_dont_panic_a441da99:

    # "Kenji groans and covers his face with his hands."
    "健二は唸って顔を手で覆う。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:163
translate jp a1_sunday_dont_panic_ed018a07:

    # ke "Agh, no, no! I can't do it. They'll eat me alive out there, I know it."
    ke "んな、無理、無理！　そんなことできるか。外のあいつらに踊り食いにされちまう。わかるんだ"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:165
translate jp a1_sunday_dont_panic_9bcae57d:

    # "That has to be a joke, but he said it with such a straight face. Relatively straight."
    "こんなの冗談に決まってる。しかし奴はまじめな顔で言っていた。割とまじめだ。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:170
translate jp a1_sunday_dont_panic_97d6e8a5:

    # ke "What are you going to do? We should hang out in here, you can help me build my fort. We might still make it if we work together."
    ke "お前こそ今日は予定あるのか？　一緒にここにいようぜ、俺の要塞建設を手伝ってくれよ。一緒にやれば、まだ間に合うかもしれない"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:180
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_0c053463:

    # hi "I wonder… I'm kinda hungry, but I made this deal that I try to take better care of myself. Be healthier, you know."
    hi "そうだなあ……腹減ってる感じだけど、体を大事にするって約束しちゃったからな。健康増進、てやつ"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:182
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_a0ce44a2:

    # hi "Dunno if I should steer clear of the takoyaki, or head straight in."
    hi "たこ焼きはよしたほうがいいのか、それとも直行すべきか。どうしようかなあ"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:187
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_456eb356:

    # ke "Deal? Sounds ominous. So what are you getting in return?"
    ke "約束？　なんか不吉な感じだな。見返りはなんなんだ？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:189
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_e7ea7ea9:

    # hi "Nothing, I guess? It's not that kind of a deal."
    hi "何もない、と思うけど？　見返りとか、そういう約束じゃないよ"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:191
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_a0625dbf:

    # hi "You know Emi, from our year? We kinda agreed to watch each other's backs and…"
    hi "同じ学年の笑美って知ってるだろ？　共闘を約束したっていうか"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:196
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_4eaa1eb3:

    # ke "Aieeeeeeee!"
    ke "ひいいいいいいいいい！"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:198
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_cb2817dd:

    # "The shrill scream and the expression of abject terror in Kenji's face chill my blood. It's as if I told a Catholic priest I sold my soul to the devil."
    "恐怖に染まった健二の顔と、急に飛び出した金切り声に背筋が凍る。『悪魔に魂を売りました』と告白されたカトリックの聖職者みたいな反応だ。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:200
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_1f354ce7:

    # ke "Her! You sold your soul to the devil, and didn't get anything in return?"
    ke "笑美だって！　お前悪魔に魂を売って、しかも何ももらわなかったってことか？！"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:202
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_6256be21:

    # ke "What the hell is wrong with you, man?"
    ke "お前、一体どうしたんだよ？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:204
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_c0bb3d9b:

    # ke "Do you know who you are dealing with?"
    ke "自分の関わってる相手が誰だかわかってるのか？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:206
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_28d15e7e:

    # ke "She's a public health danger. Do you know how many people she sends to the hospital monthly with her carefully placed flying tackles?"
    ke "あいつは歩く危険物だぞ。あいつのピンポイントな高速タックルで毎月どれだけの人間が病院送りにされてるか知らないのか？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:211
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_d5f5a63c:

    # ke "She's one of them! A key player in the vast conspiracy that aims for the complete submission of everything that is manly."
    ke "あいつも奴らの仲間だ！　男らしいものはすべて服従させようとする巨大な陰謀の中心人物だ"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:213
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_01556351:

    # ke "I can't believe what I'm hearing. I trusted in your judgment, man. I thought we were brothers."
    ke "今聞いてることが信じられない。俺はお前の判断力を信じてたんだぞ。俺たちは仲間だと思ってたのに"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:215
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_dce3f7d2:

    # ke "You have to call it off before it's too late."
    ke "手遅れになる前にやめるんだ"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:217
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_e0547e62:

    # ke "This festival too; it's just one of their ploys."
    ke "学園祭もそうだ。あいつらの策略の一部なんだぞ"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:223
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_430f2fd4:

    # "It's kinda unsettling, and now I start to feel doubtful, myself."
    "なんだか落ち着かない。今度はこっちまで疑わしい気分になり始める。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:225
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_1ea23339:

    # "Should I bother going?"
    "わざわざ行くべきだろうか？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:227
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_066560c3:

    # "I've got a book I've been meaning to read."
    "読もうと思っている本もある。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:229
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_f7161674:

    # "Something about an underground postal system that may or may not exist."
    "存在するかどうかもわからない、アングラな郵便網に関する本だ。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:231
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_b945009c:

    # "It's short, too. I could have it finished in a day."
    "短いし、一日で読み終えることができるだろう。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:233
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_d146d39d:

    # "But would that be a good way to spend my time?"
    "だけど、そんなことをして時間をつぶしてていいんだろうか？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:235
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_daa02b75:

    # "Well, yeah. It definitely would be."
    "まぁ、そうだな。当然いいに決まってる。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:237
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_11e20a95:

    # "But I suppose that it would probably be a better idea to head outside."
    "でも、外に出るのがもっといい考えだろう。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:239
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_669bd374:

    # "See the festival."
    "学園祭を見に行くんだ。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:241
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_6352bfb2:

    # "Try to integrate with all the other sideshow acts."
    "他の屋台なんかの出し物を適当に見て回るとするか。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:243
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_dfa7b5c6:

    # "Honestly, I should at least make an attempt to keep up the somewhat friendly personality I've had the past week."
    "マジな話、俺はこの一週間、どっちかというと愛想のいいキャラを保ってきた。せめてそれを崩さないための努力くらいはした方がいい。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:245
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_35b8121e:

    # "Maybe get something to eat, my stomach suggests."
    "何か食べ物を取ってこいよ、と俺の胃が言っている。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:247
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_6f0ed2c2:

    # "It's almost lunchtime… I could at least grab something from one of the stalls outside."
    "もう昼食時だ……外の屋台で何か買い漁るくらいはできるだろう。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:256
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_dd2e5805:

    # "I'm soon outside, surrounded by various students and people who may or may not be their parents."
    "すぐに外に出ると、いろんな生徒たちと、その親かもしれない人たちに取り囲まれる。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:258
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_15d244c9:

    # "Every so often I catch a glimpse of someone who clearly just came up from town for the promise of a festival."
    "ときどき、きっと街から学園祭を見にやってきたんだな、という人がちらっと目に留まる。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:260
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_eaeead98:

    # "They're easy to spot."
    "そういう人たちは、見れば一目でわかる。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:262
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_daf8f93c:

    # "The ones who can't stop staring, and behind their eyes you can tell they're thinking 'Now, what's wrong with {b}this{/b} one?'"
    "じろじろ見ずにはいられない人たち――その目の奥には、こんな考えが透けて見える。『で、{b}この{/b}生徒はどこが悪いんだ？』と。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:264
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_edc92488:

    # "I almost want to yell at them."
    "思わず大声で怒鳴りつけてやりたくなる。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:266
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_cf2a0093:

    # "But at the same time, can I deny that I've been doing the same thing all week?"
    "でもその一方で、俺自身も一週間ずっと同じことをしていなかったといえるだろうか？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:268
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_49354b6a:

    # "A wave of something like disgust sweeps over me; guilt for my own narrow-mindedness."
    "嫌悪感みたいな波が押し寄せてくる――俺自身の偏狭さへの罪悪感だ。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:270
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_ce617998:

    # "…"
    "……"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:277
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_8380bfa9:

    # "I push the thoughts aside, concentrating on the pangs of hunger that burn my guts like a wildfire."
    "そんな思索を脇に押しやって、空腹のせいで、胃が野火のようにひりひりと痛むのに意識を集中させる。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:279
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_5a8dcc95:

    # "The scent of something fried leads me to the promised land, where I can get some lunch."
    "何かの揚げられる香りが俺を約束の地――食事の買える場所へと導く。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:283
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_86905033:

    # "I'm just getting my order when a loud voice interrupts me."
    "ちょうど注文したものが出てくるところで、大きな声で呼び止められる。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:292
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_9b21ec50:

    # emi "Hey, what the hell are you doing?"
    emi "ちょっと、それどういうつもり？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:296
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_b826a075:

    # hi "Having break— er, lunch."
    hi "朝――じゃない、昼飯を食べようとしてんだよ"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:301
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_6737719b:

    # emi "Breakfast?"
    emi "朝ごはん？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:306
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_adf21eae:

    # emi "You mean you just got up?"
    emi "今起きたばっかりってこと？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:308
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_c7d93a97:

    # hi "Er…"
    hi "えっと……"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:310
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_70a63897:

    # "Suddenly sleeping all morning feels like a crime."
    "突然、朝寝坊してたことが犯罪みたいに感じられてくる。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:312
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_0932c741:

    # hi "No, I meant lunch… honest."
    hi "いや、昼飯って言ったんだよ……マジで"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:314
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_10006c17:

    # "She's not buying it."
    "笑美は信じていない。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:316
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_0c4f4527:

    # hi "Brunch?"
    hi "ブランチかな？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:321
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_e51ad968:

    # emi "That's not a healthy breakfast at all!"
    emi "そんな朝ご飯、全然健康的じゃないよ！"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:323
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_722f5d62:

    # "She snatches my food out of my hand and glares at me."
    "笑美は俺の食事をひったくると、こちらをにらみつける。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:325
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_5b52bf01:

    # "What the hell is this girl doing?"
    "どういうつもりだよ、こいつ？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:327
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_9d4a2377:

    # hi "Hey, that's my breakfast!"
    hi "おい、それ俺の朝飯だぞ！"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:332
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_9906bcf7:

    # emi "What happened to it being your lunch?"
    emi "お昼ごはんじゃなかったの？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:334
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_69af82c9:

    # hi "That's my… whatever, it's my food!"
    hi "それ俺の……とにかく、俺の飯だっつーの！"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:336
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_149678f8:

    # "Emi places her hands on her hips and begins lecturing me."
    "笑美は両手を腰に当てると、説教を始める。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:341
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_bd25f0b7:

    # emi "Did you really forget your dietary plan already?"
    emi "食事プランのこと、ホントにもう忘れちゃったの？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:343
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_abaf6d9a:

    # emi "You need to be more conscious of your health, Hisao!"
    emi "もっと健康に気をつけなきゃ、久夫くん！"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:348
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_48ce0ca0:

    # emi "What about your heart?"
    emi "心臓はどうなのよ？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:350
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_adf10237:

    # hi "My heart's fine the way it is! Mostly."
    hi "心臓は別に問題ないよ！　だいたいは"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:352
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_f290908d:

    # "All I get in response is a roll of the eyes."
    "返事の代わりに、笑美はあきれたように視線を上向ける。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:357
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_9c689993:

    # emi "I doubt that."
    emi "どうだか"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:362
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_bfcced41:

    # emi "You wouldn't be here if that was the case, would you?"
    emi "問題がなかったら、この学校には来てないでしょ？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:364
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_446c3277:

    # "The girl's got a point, of course."
    "確かに、この子はいいところを突いている。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:366
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_9367a558:

    # "But I'm not about to concede it."
    "だけど、こっちとしても譲歩するつもりはない。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:368
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_589d0b59:

    # hi "It's not that bad of a heart!"
    hi "別にそんなに心臓が悪いわけじゃないって！"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:370
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_7f10b749:

    # hi "Certainly it can handle a little grease now and again!"
    hi "たまにちょっとだけ脂っこいものを食べるくらい、どうってことないに決まってるだろ！"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:372
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_8a4f4ef5:

    # "Yeah, sure. And it handled a little running just fine, too."
    "よく言うよ。ちょっとランニングしただけでへばったくせに。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:377
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_35dbeb2a:

    # "Emi seems unconvinced."
    "笑美は納得してないようだ。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:379
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_115d9729:

    # "Not surprising, as I haven't even managed to convince myself."
    "そりゃそうだろう。俺だって納得していない。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:381
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_9dbce6d7:

    # emi "Maybe, but not if you're sleeping the day away all the time!"
    emi "そうかもね。だけど、いつも真っ昼間まで寝てるようなら話は別！"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:383
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_95c08626:

    # "A devious look suddenly crosses her face."
    "突然、笑美の顔に何か企むような表情がよぎる。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:388
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_bc0101ff:

    # emi "Of course, if you'd been following a routine from the beginning you wouldn't be in this situation…"
    emi "そもそも、最初から日課の運動をちゃんとこなしてたら、こんなことにはなってないわけだし……"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:392
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_64a76345:

    # hi "Hey, I've had a pretty eventful week, you know!"
    hi "あのさ、今週は本当にいろいろあったんだって！"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:394
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_936b62a7:

    # hi "For example, I almost died! And there was a lot of meeting people, and then I was on a roof for a while…"
    hi "たとえばさ、俺は危うく死ぬところだったんだぞ！　あと人にいっぱい会ったし、屋上でしばらく過ごしたし……"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:399
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_cfa4ac8e:

    # emi "Which is no excuse for slacking off, you know."
    emi "そういうの、サボりの言い訳にはならないでしょ"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:401
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_d488a880:

    # emi "A little near death experience is no excuse for skipping basic exercise."
    emi "ちょっと死にかけたからって、基礎体力作りを怠けていいことにはならないの"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:406
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_23a149b3:

    # emi "Like running in the mornings."
    emi "朝のランニングとかね"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:408
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_41033b5c:

    # "She nods, as if something important has just been decided."
    "笑美は、ちょうど今重要なことが決まったみたいにうなずく。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:415
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_d29fc21e:

    # emi "So it's settled, then!"
    emi "じゃ、これで決まりってことで！"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:420
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_7e9b7694:

    # emi "You've seen the error of your ways and are willing to adhere to my routine, right?"
    emi "久夫くんは、自分のやり方が間違ってたって認めて、あたしの日課をちゃんと守るんだよね？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:422
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_3e7b825d:

    # emi "I'll see you bright and early in the morning?"
    emi "明日朝早くに会えるんだよね？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:427
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_3b8549ce:

    # emi "We'll be running buddies?"
    emi "一緒に走ってくれるんだよね？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:429
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_7c76f8e9:

    # hi "You know, you'd already convinced me yesterday that this was a good idea."
    hi "あのさ、それがいい考えだってのは昨日ちゃんとわかったから"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:431
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_6ac8693d:

    # hi "You don't need to convince me again."
    hi "何度も説得してくれなくていいって"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:433
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_3fb2f547:

    # "Not that I did a good job of being convinced."
    "すんなりと説得されたわけじゃなかったんだけど。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:435
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_642d2be2:

    # "She's right about eating healthy, after all. And here I am ordering up something grossly unhealthy."
    "健康的な食生活を送るべき――笑美の言うことはなんだかんだいって正しい。なのに今、俺はひどく不健康なものを注文している。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:437
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_7a958daf:

    # "But delicious!"
    "おいしいんだけどな！"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:439
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_d1199061:

    # "There are more important things than deliciousness, aren't there?"
    "おいしさより大事なことなんてないんじゃないか？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:441
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_e0161948:

    # "Like staying alive?"
    "生きることくらいか？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:443
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_8e133743:

    # "If Emi weren't here browbeating me for my poor decisions, I'd probably…"
    "もし笑美がここで俺のひどい判断を叱りつけてくれなかったら、俺はたぶん……"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:445
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_14b2874b:

    # "Hey, wait a second."
    "いや、ちょっと待てよ。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:447
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_1dfb1b7c:

    # "A sudden question springs to mind."
    "突然、疑問が心に浮かぶ。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:449
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_f36aa9b7:

    # hi "Hey, why the hell have you taken such an interest in my well-being?"
    hi "あのさ、なんで俺の健康のこと、そんなに心配するんだ？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:454
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_7372120d:

    # "Emi shrugs and grins at me."
    "笑美は肩をすくめて笑みを見せる。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:459
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_b34f1cf2:

    # emi "You're the new guy."
    emi "久夫くん、転校生じゃない"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:461
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_52b25bc2:

    # emi "I figure you don't have any friends yet, right?"
    emi "たぶん友達もまだいないでしょ、違う？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:466
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_d9fc3094:

    # emi "Besides, I've caused you trouble all week, right?"
    emi "それに、今週ずっと迷惑かけちゃったでしょ？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:468
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_67fba381:

    # emi "I owe you for not getting angry."
    emi "怒らないで付き合ってくれた借りもあるし"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:473
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_482a8e67:

    # emi "And I told the nurse I would, anyway."
    emi "あと、ナースくんにも約束しちゃったし"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:475
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_2e762dff:

    # "Uh… huh. Crazy little running girl wants to make me healthy."
    "そう……なんだ。この小さくて走るのが大好きな女の子は、俺に健康になって欲しいんだ。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:477
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_9075ebf5:

    # "Well, I suppose there are worse fates."
    "まぁ、このくらいならどうってことはないか。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:479
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_3be34344:

    # hi "Okay, that sounds… fine."
    hi "わかったよ、そりゃ……そうだよな"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:481
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_1b48c4bd:

    # hi "Thanks for your concern."
    hi "気にかけてくれてありがとう"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:483
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_fab85d1b:

    # hi "Tomorrow morning, then?"
    hi "じゃあ、明日の朝ってことでいいな？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:490
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_dbd12d3e:

    # "I figure that ends the conversation, so I turn to leave."
    "これで話は終わりだと思い、背を向けて立ち去ろうとする。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:492
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_90fba6d1:

    # emi "Not so fast!"
    emi "ちょっと待って！"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:497
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_b296c8d7:

    # "I feel a hand on my collar and in a second I've been yanked backwards."
    "襟を手で掴まれたと思ったら、後ろに引っ張られる。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:499
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_16afd130:

    # hi "Hey, no need to be so rough!"
    hi "おい、そんな乱暴にするなって！"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:501
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_efa025e7:

    # hi "What do you want now?"
    hi "今度はなんだよ？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:506
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_6db6350c:

    # "Emi looks almost wounded by my annoyed question."
    "いらつき混じりの質問に、笑美はだいぶ傷ついているようだ。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:508
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_6c80dc4a:

    # emi "Thought you could use the company."
    emi "付き合ってあげた方がいいんじゃないかって思って"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:513
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_5d39db5f:

    # "Her eyes narrow."
    "笑美の目が細められる。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:515
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_77dc4d61:

    # emi "Besides, you were just going to try sneaking some more of that fried crap, weren't you?"
    emi "それに、これからまた揚げものなんかをこっそり食べに行くつもりだったんでしょ？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:517
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_ee54a467:

    # "Well, I wasn't going to, but now that she mentions it that would have been a really good idea."
    "いや、そんなつもりはなかったんだけど、言われてみればそれもいい考えかもしれない。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:519
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_6976a9c0:

    # hi "I was not!"
    hi "んなことないって！"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:524
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_c9f0b103:

    # "Another glare."
    "またにらみつけられる。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:526
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_f0c642c1:

    # hi "Okay, maybe I was going to get a little…"
    hi "ごめん、少しくらい買おうかなと……"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:528
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_22bc7b58:

    # "The glare continues."
    "まだにらみつけられてる。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:530
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_6dfe47e8:

    # hi "Okay, a lot."
    hi "ごめん、たくさん"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:532
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_d77e95c5:

    # "Jesus, I'm a danger to myself and others, aren't I?"
    "おいおい、俺のやってることって自分にとっても他人にとっても危険なんじゃないか。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:534
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_b8fe7a2c:

    # "I get done agreeing that I need to be healthier, and then immediately start considering the next unhealthy habit that comes my way."
    "もっと健康にならなきゃいけないって納得したそばから、すぐ次の不健康な習慣のことを考え始めてるなんて。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:539
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_b4a0a08b:

    # emi "I knew it! You can't be trusted."
    emi "やっぱりね！　ホント信用できないんだから"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:544
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_52d7786d:

    # emi "Now I definitely have to stick with you."
    emi "これはもう、ずっとついてないとダメみたいだね"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:546
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_a4915d83:

    # "This whole situation feels silly."
    "バカみたいなシチュエーションだ。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:548
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_ff5c08c8:

    # "I can only imagine what passersby think of the sight of me being lectured by a tiny girl half my size."
    "通行人に、俺の半分くらいしかない小さな女の子から説教されてる姿を見られたら、どう思われるだろう。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:550
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_7efa9bc8:

    # "Maybe I should just give up for now."
    "そろそろあきらめた方がいいかもしれない。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:552
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_b8283036:

    # hi "Fine, do what you like."
    hi "わかったよ、好きにしてくれ"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:554
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_3f739ce1:

    # "I sigh."
    "俺はため息をつく。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:556
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_6c394094:

    # "Might as well make the best of this."
    "こういう状況でも、やれるだけのことはやってみよう。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:558
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_6c1570a5:

    # hi "What do you want to do?"
    hi "何がしたいんだ？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:563
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_c322dbb9:

    # "Emi thinks for a minute."
    "笑美は少し考え込む。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:565
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_436babf7:

    # emi "Well, I promised Rin I'd stop by her mural…"
    emi "うーん、壁画のとこに行くって琳に約束したから……"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:570
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_1dedc83e:

    # emi "So let's do that!"
    emi "じゃあ、それでいこうよ！"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:572
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_ac2fceac:

    # "I confess I'm slightly curious as to how her mural turned out myself, so again I consider there are worse fates."
    "正直、俺としても壁画がどうなったのかちょっと興味がある。だからさっきと同じで、このくらいならどうってことはない。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:580
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_8e3c3c13:

    # "I give a nod of assent and find myself almost dragged bodily through the crowd as Emi races to our destination."
    "うなずいて同意すると、笑美は目的地へ向かって突っ走り、俺は入場者たちの間をほとんど体ごと引きずり回されている。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:588
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_2820f650:

    # "By the time we reach the dorms, I can feel my heart pounding."
    "寮にたどりつくころには、心臓がバクバク言っているのがわかる。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:590
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_de69cd93:

    # "My heart shouldn't be pounding after just that."
    "たったこれくらいで動悸がするなんておかしいだろう。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:592
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_3055f416:

    # "I take a few deep breaths, willing myself to calm down."
    "体を落ち着かせるために、何度か深呼吸をする。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:594
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_4e15c2c8:

    # "I'm one of the most normal looking people in the school, but I still have to be here."
    "俺はこの学校で見た目が一番普通な部類に属してるけど、やっぱりここにいなきゃならないんだ。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:596
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_8cd6312d:

    # "Sometimes I almost wish I'd lost a hand or something."
    "ときどき、いっそ手か何かをなくしていたらよかったのにと思いそうになる。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:598
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_1b7e2aee:

    # "At least then it'd be obvious that I belong."
    "それだったら少なくとも周りから浮いてはいないはずだ。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:600
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_afca18ec:

    # "But instead I don't even look sick."
    "でも実際はそうじゃなくて、俺は病気にすら見えない。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:602
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_683e94ea:

    # "Even now, trying to catch my breath, I just look out of shape."
    "呼吸を整えようとしてる今でさえ、単に具合が悪そうに見えるだけだ。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:604
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_c4f9315b:

    # "Emi looks back and notices my state of distress."
    "笑美は振り向いて、俺の不調に気づく。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:613
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_612f99b4:

    # emi "You're not going to die on me, are you?"
    emi "まさか、あたしの眼の前で死んだりしないよね？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:618
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_8cc98fa7:

    # emi "Please don't!"
    emi "お願い、死なないでよ！"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:623
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_39d317e0:

    # emi "It'll be all my fault, and I don't want to deal with that kind of guilt."
    emi "そしたらみんなあたしのせいになっちゃう。そんな寝覚めが悪いの、いやだよ"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:625
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_86684648:

    # emi "Besides, after the last time I really don't think I need to see that again, especially because the nurse will totally say it's all my fault."
    emi "それに、この前あんなことがあった後だし、ほんとに勘弁だよ。絶対ナースくんに、みんなあたしが悪いって言われちゃう"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:629
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_ca020249:

    # hi "N… nah, I'm fine."
    hi "い……いや、大丈夫だから"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:631
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_b34ba595:

    # hi "Guess I need to start running after all."
    hi "やっぱランニング、始めた方がいいみたいだな"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:636
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_20361b7e:

    # emi "And you wanted to keep eating your greasy… whatever it was."
    emi "でも久夫くん、なんだか知らないけど脂っこいものを食べたがってたよね"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:641
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_e52cd076:

    # emi "See? It's a good thing I found you, right?"
    emi "ね？　あたしと出会ってよかったでしょ？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:643
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_05353a99:

    # "Yes it was."
    "まったくだ。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:645
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_da9749d8:

    # hi "Maybe."
    hi "かもな"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:650
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_b9d4395c:

    # "Of course I don't add that I wouldn't be in this state if she hadn't dragged me across the festival grounds."
    "もちろん、笑美に学園祭会場を引きずり回されたりしなければこんなことにならなかったってことは、付け加えたりしなかった。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:652
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_47c9e7e9:

    # "Further conversation is interrupted by the sudden appearance of Rin."
    "琳が突然現れて、その先の会話は中断される。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:662
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_9e289074:

    # rin "Oh, it's you."
    rin "ああ、君たちか"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:672
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_b9cf099d:

    # rin "Hello Emi."
    rin "こんちは、笑美"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:677
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_a5f97b3f:

    # emi "Hey Rin! I brought Hisao along because he was going to give himself a heart attack!"
    emi "こんちは、琳！　久夫くんが心臓発作を起こしそうになったから、連れてきたよ！"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:682
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_6976a9c0_1:

    # hi "I was not!"
    hi "んなことないって！"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:684
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_6a27d26f:

    # "My objection goes unnoticed."
    "俺の抗議は無視される。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:689
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_4c3b554b:

    # emi "We stopped by to see how the mural turned out!"
    emi "壁画がどうなったか見たくて寄ったんだ！"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:691
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_c5e7c631:

    # "Rin nods slowly."
    "琳はゆっくりうなずく。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:696
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_a43e1c0b:

    # rin "Well, it's right there."
    rin "あぁ、あっちだよ"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:701
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_34e09203:

    # rin "You can see it pretty clearly."
    rin "よく見えるよね"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:703
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_322b04ff:

    # "I find myself wondering how long Rin's been standing here in front of the mural."
    "気がつくと考えている――琳はここで、壁画の前にどのくらい立っていたんだろう。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:705
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_7416fed4:

    # "Has anyone even stopped by to look at it?"
    "今まで一人でも、立ち止まってちゃんと壁画を見た人はいたんだろうか？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:707
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_d9884000:

    # "Are we the first ones?"
    "俺たちが一番最初なのか？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:709
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_2ea9cc79:

    # "Obviously we're not the first to see it, of course."
    "もちろんどう考えたって、壁画を目にするのは俺たちが最初じゃない。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:711
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_8baf03b3:

    # "I mean, it's pretty big."
    "というか、壁画はすごく大きい。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:713
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_72cfaa6f:

    # "You'd be hard-pressed not to see it."
    "目に入らないわけがない。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:715
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_0b256c10:

    # "At the same time, I don't think anyone's actually talked to Rin about it."
    "その一方で、誰も壁画のことで実際に琳に話しかけたとは思えない。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:717
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_1f28be51:

    # "Anyone but us, that is."
    "俺たち以外には、ってことだ。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:719
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_e7c4221e:

    # "I feel compelled to say something."
    "何か言わなきゃならない気がする。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:721
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_2f037c7d:

    # hi "It looks pretty good."
    hi "すごくいいな"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:726
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_dbea88f0:

    # rin "I'm still not happy with how it turned out."
    rin "まだ出来映えには満足してないんだ"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:728
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_c51a09d2:

    # rin "But I guess it'll do."
    rin "だけど、こんなものかな"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:730
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_4e7128bc:

    # "She seems almost resigned to it."
    "琳はほとんどあきらめてしまっているみたいだ。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:732
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_b12b6582:

    # "I'm not sure what she expected as a result, but I guess she didn't quite get there."
    "どういう出来上がりを考えていたのかはわからないけど、でも思った通りにはならなかったんだろう。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:739
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_ef4ba76c:

    # "We stand in front of the mural, taking it all in."
    "俺たちは壁画の前に立って、その全容を理解しようとする。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:741
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_7af9e0f9:

    # "I try my best to concentrate on the composition of the thing."
    "俺は壁画の構図に集中しようと全力を尽くす。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:743
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_eed0bb08:

    # "It's actually fairly interesting."
    "実際、かなり興味深い。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:745
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_57f99cf0:

    # "The colors swoop and blend together, dragging me along with them."
    "色が突然まじりあって、俺はその中に引きずり込まれてしまう。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:747
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_bf6552ac:

    # "There's a dreamlike quality to the whole thing that makes me almost feel sleepy."
    "何もかもに夢みたいにおぼろげな質感があって、思わず眠くなってしまうくらいだ。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:749
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_c8978bae:

    # "I try hunting out some of the colors Emi and I grabbed for her."
    "笑美と俺が取ってきてやった色を見つけようとする。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:751
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_f248fe6e:

    # "Try as I might, I can't see any Prussian Blue."
    "頑張ってみても、プルシアンブルーは見つからない。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:753
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_2521d867:

    # "Oh well."
    "ああ、そうだ。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:755
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_ed87218a:

    # "I'm sure it's in there somewhere."
    "どこかにあることは確かなんだけど。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:762
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_136e1091:

    # "My feet start to hurt, but Rin doesn't seem inclined to move on."
    "俺の足が痛み始めても、琳は動こうとしない。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:764
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_ecffd02e:

    # "Emi speaks up."
    "笑美が口を開く。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:769
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_50e1fec2:

    # emi "Hey Rin, have you eaten?"
    emi "ねぇ琳、何か食べた？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:774
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_7f9793a8:

    # rin "Of course. You can't survive otherwise."
    rin "当然。食べなきゃ生きていけないよ"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:779
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_edad0aad:

    # emi "What about in the past five hours?"
    emi "じゃあ、５時間以内には？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:784
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_65b95bbc:

    # rin "Maybe. But I'm hungry again, so maybe that means I'm wrong."
    rin "たぶん食べたよ。でもまたお腹すいてるし、勘違いかもしれない"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:789
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_c55a831a:

    # "Emi grins and claps her hands together."
    "笑美はにっこり笑って、両手を打ち合わせる。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:794
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_63399c73:

    # emi "Good! Come get some food with us!"
    emi "そっか！　じゃあ一緒に食べ物買いに行こうよ！"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:796
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_b6f5b38d:

    # "Rin nods in assent."
    "琳はうなずいて同意する。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:801
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_4491b8a0:

    # rin "Okay, but we should hurry before they notice I'm gone."
    rin "いいよ。あの人たちにいなくなったって気づかれないように、急がないとね"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:803
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_60d4beb8:

    # "Somehow I don't think they'd care."
    "たぶん、気にしないと思う。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:805
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_0be2006f:

    # "Whoever they are."
    "あの人たちってのが誰なのかは知らないけど。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:816
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_c29b264e:

    # "As we head back to the food stalls, I cast a longing eye over the fried food."
    "屋台に戻ると、俺は揚げ物に恋焦がれるような視線を投げかける。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:818
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_353363a6:

    # "No, I'd better not."
    "いや、やめておいた方がいい。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:820
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_73bbc4c2:

    # "I'm pretty sure Emi wouldn't let me, anyway."
    "どうせ、笑美が許してくれるわけがないんだから。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:831
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_c2a81e52:

    # "We find a nice spot on the grass and sit down to eat our purchases."
    "芝生にいい穴場を見つけて座り、それぞれに買ってきたものを食べる。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:833
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_fed089d4:

    # "Well, my purchases, anyway. Somehow I've wound up paying for all the food."
    "というか、俺が買ってきたんだけど。なぜか食べ物の代金を俺が全部払うことになってしまった。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:835
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_5d38f6ae:

    # "Surprisingly, my (unfried) food is pretty good."
    "びっくりしたことに、俺の食べ物（揚げてない）はとてもおいしい。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:837
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_e1ef2e0c:

    # "Silence falls as Emi and I eat and Rin stares at… something or other, occasionally eating a bite or two of her food."
    "笑美と俺が食べるあいだ、琳はじっと……あちこちを見つめ、ときどき一口二口自分の食べ物を口にする。沈黙が降りる。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:839
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_cf977a97:

    # "I finish my meal first, and lay back on the grass."
    "俺は一番先に食事を終え、芝生に寝転がる。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:841
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_93ef0e78:

    # "Emi glances up from her food."
    "笑美が食べ物からちらりと顔を上げる。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:846
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_f2424c6e:

    # emi "Tired, Hisao?"
    emi "疲れた、久夫くん？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:848
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_9ba59f5f:

    # hi "A little, I guess."
    hi "ちょっと、かな"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:853
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_6c052e9f:

    # emi "Well, don't oversleep or anything tomorrow morning."
    emi "ねぇ、明日の朝、寝過ごしたりしちゃダメだからね"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:858
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_9c419825:

    # emi "We start our morning runs, remember?"
    emi "朝のランニング始めるんだよ、覚えてる？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:860
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_5d372ce7:

    # "Actually, they'd slipped my mind."
    "実は、すっかり忘れていた。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:862
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_6fabd62f:

    # "I was actually just enjoying myself."
    "俺は、実のところただ楽しんでいたんだ。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:864
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_18390310:

    # "Wandering around the festival with these two has actually been fun."
    "この二人と学園祭をぶらつくのは意外と楽しかった。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:866
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_1f9dc14e:

    # hi "Yeah, I'll set an alarm."
    hi "ああ、目覚ましをセットしておくよ"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:871
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_a2983878:

    # emi "You'd better be there!"
    emi "来ないとダメだからね！"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:876
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_05fa394d:

    # emi "I'll get angry if you aren't!"
    emi "来なかったら怒るよ！"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:878
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_00b9a429:

    # hi "God forbid."
    hi "そうならないように、神様に祈っとくか"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:883
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_df7aec0a:

    # rin "I don't think God comes into it."
    rin "神様は関係ないと思う"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:888
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_78daa583:

    # rin "Unless there's some kind of freak accident and your alarm clock shorts out."
    rin "何か変なアクシデントが起きて、目覚まし時計がショートしなければ、だけど"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:893
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_c8c509b8:

    # rin "That might be a random act of God."
    rin "そういうのって、神様の気まぐれかもしんないね"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:898
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_55f8a1c0:

    # emi "Well don't cause any random acts of God, then."
    emi "じゃあそんな気まぐれなんて起こさないでよね"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:900
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_77dcced4:

    # "A plan forms itself in my mind."
    "一つの計画が、頭の中で形をなす。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:902
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_5d999a22:

    # "It's a plan that makes me feel kind of guilty, but I throw it into execution anyway."
    "ちょっと罪悪感を感じないでもない計画だけど、とにかくやってみよう。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:904
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_fe7c1d46:

    # "Dammit, I've earned a little fried food."
    "ちくしょう、少しくらい揚げ物食べたっていいじゃないか。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:906
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_d0e885de:

    # "And anyway, I'm going to start running tomorrow, right?"
    "それにどっちにしても、明日から走り始めるんだろ？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:908
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_a0d3524a:

    # "So the actual routine all starts then, not now."
    "だから、本当の日課は今じゃなくて、全部その時に始まるんだ。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:910
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_c99a458e:

    # "Ergo, the dietary portion starts tomorrow too, ergo I can have something unhealthy today."
    "ゆえに食事制限が始まるのは明日からであり、それゆえ今日は不健康なものを食べても構わないということだ。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:912
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_9fad3e29:

    # "A sort of final farewell to all the stuff I used to eat with wild abandon before the hospital."
    "病院に入る前、好き放題に食べていたあらゆるものへの最後の別れとでもいうかな。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:914
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_a9e65355:

    # hi "Actually, I suppose I should head back to my room."
    hi "実はさ、部屋に戻ろうと思うんだ"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:916
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_61621b3a:

    # hi "I had some homework to do, and if I'm going to run in the morning I should make it an early night…"
    hi "宿題があったし、明日走るつもりなら、今夜は早く寝ないと……"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:921
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_69a94375:

    # "Those narrowed eyes again."
    "笑美がまた目を細める。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:926
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_fba58ab0:

    # emi "You sure you're not just going to sneak off and buy some of that fried stuff over there?"
    emi "あそこでこっそり揚げもの買ったりしないよね？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:928
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_01b13f0f:

    # hi "Nah, I'm too full to bother now."
    hi "いやあ、お腹いっぱいでそんなことする気にならないよ"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:930
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_ec1a311d:

    # "I pat my stomach for emphasis."
    "お腹を叩いて強調してみせる。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:932
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_86172257:

    # hi "Besides, you two have cleaned me out anyway."
    hi "それに、お前らのせいで一文無しになっちゃったしな"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:937
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_80b48e0e:

    # "Emi giggles. It's a surprisingly pleasant sound."
    "笑美はくすくす笑う。びっくりするくらい心地いい声だ。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:939
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_9294a3e7:

    # "Another pang of guilt."
    "またしても痛みのような罪悪感。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:941
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_97151293:

    # "She's got to know that I'm lying to her, doesn't she?"
    "笑美は、俺が嘘をついてることに気づいてるはずだろ。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:943
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_c5105595:

    # "Or is she just that trusting?"
    "それとも、そんなに信じやすいだけなのか？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:945
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_70d70679:

    # "I feel kind of like a monster."
    "なんだか極悪人みたいな気分になる。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:950
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_7c9a985a:

    # emi "All part of my master plan, Hisao."
    emi "これもあたしの計画のうちだよ、久夫くん"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:955
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_ffd5b041:

    # emi "Well, I guess I'll see you tomorrow morning then."
    emi "じゃあ、また明日の朝に会おうね"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:960
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_2010c0db:

    # emi "Thanks for the food! And for keeping us company!"
    emi "ごちそうさま！　あとあたしたちと付き合ってくれてありがと！"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:962
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_54ff242e:

    # "And here I thought she was doing me a favor."
    "こっちは笑美が俺に付き合ってくれてると思ってたんだけどな。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:967
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_95e044b7:

    # "Rin nods in agreement."
    "琳はうなずいて同意すると、足を俺に向けて振る。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:969
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_f26317b6:

    # rin "I won't say 'See you tomorrow' because that would be like predicting the future, and I'm pretty sure I can't do that."
    rin "『また明日』とは言わないよ。それって未来を予知するみたいなもので、私にはそんなことできないからね"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:971
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_35c4f685:

    # hi "…"
    hi "……"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:973
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_16a7dec2:

    # hi "Okay."
    hi "そっか"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:975
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_e66d6dda:

    # hi "Bye, you two."
    hi "じゃあな、二人とも"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:977
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_237ae67b:

    # "I feel oddly glad that I decided to leave my room today."
    "変なことだけど、今日部屋を出る決心をしてよかった。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:979
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_d1a733cc:

    # "Not a bad way to start my second week here, I suppose."
    "ここでの二週目のスタートとしては悪くないだろう。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:987
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_569c17c0:

    # "Once I'm sure I'm out of Emi's line of sight, I make a beeline for the food stands and buy some cake."
    "笑美の視界から外れているのを確認すると、俺は屋台へと直行してケーキを買う。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:989
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_1cfd84d2:

    # "At least it's not fried, right?"
    "少なくとも、揚げものじゃないよな？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:991
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_bc4120bf:

    # "That's slightly better than what I was planning to do."
    "最初の予定よりも少しマシになってる。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:993
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_d33ec5f5:

    # "I still feel a little bad about lying to Emi, though."
    "笑美に嘘をついてしまって、まだちょっと悪いとは思ってるけど。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:995
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_ae52ca95:

    # "She really does seem concerned about my health."
    "あいつ、俺の健康のことを心の底から気にかけてくれているみたいだ。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:997
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_98ab936a:

    # "I'll make it up to her somehow."
    "なんか埋め合わせをしてやらなきゃ。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:999
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_9072d857:

    # "Better head back to my room."
    "部屋に戻った方がよさそうだ。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1001
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_852f9c07:

    # "Hey, I {b}do{/b} have work to do."
    "{b}本当に{/b}しなきゃならないことがあるんだから。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1008
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_d456e34e:

    # "My book waits for me, and I flop on to my bed and read through the fireworks display."
    "今朝読もうとしていた本を手に取ると、ベッドに倒れこんで、花火大会の間じゅう読み進める。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1016
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_4ddaf194:

    # "Eventually all the walking around (or more accurately, running around) catches up with me."
    "結局、歩き回った（より正確には走り回った）のがまずかったんだ。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1018
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_0522c7ab:

    # "I really am out of shape."
    "ほんとに不健康だな、俺。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1020
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_1141061d:

    # "Emi dragging me out in the morning to run might just be a good thing after all."
    "笑美が朝ランニングに引っ張り出してくれるっていうのは、なんだかんだいって実にいいことかもしれない。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1022
translate jp a1_sunday_is_carnival_3b67e87a:

    # "It's something to look forward to."
    "楽しみなことなんだ。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1034
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_220a87bc:

    # hi "Well, I joined the art club so I guess I'll go with them."
    hi "んー、美術部に入ったからそこの人らと行くかな"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1039
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_e2a8a173:

    # ke "You did what?"
    ke "お前、何したって？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1041
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_7054f4d8:

    # hi "I joined the art club."
    hi "美術部に入った"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1046
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_bc68a40e:

    # ke "Man, that was a bad move. Really bad. You don't know what kind of girls there are in the art club. Troubled, angsty cuties who tear your heart out and eat it raw."
    ke "お前、なんてバカな真似するんだよ。大変だぞ。美術部にいる女がどんなか、わかってないだろう。不安や悩みを抱えた美少女たちが、ひとの心臓をえぐり出して生のまま食べちまうんだぞ"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1048
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_2a300f1c:

    # "Well, I know one art club member, and I don't really see Rin suddenly becoming a psychotic murderer."
    "まあ、美術部の部員は一人知ってるけど、あの琳が急に病的な殺人者になるとは思えない。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1050
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_c9b61580:

    # hi "That seems unlikely."
    hi "そりゃないな"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1052
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_286007d7:

    # ke "Don't say that. Don't fool yourself. You have no idea what you are dealing with here, man. They are the worst kind."
    ke "そういうこと言うな。自分をごまかすんじゃない。お前、自分が何を相手してるのかわかってないだろう。一番たちが悪い奴らなんだぞ"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1057
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_b3a6e440:

    # ke "They drag you in with all this fancy-pantsy shit and when you least expect it, BAM!"
    ke "派手な見かけでお前を引きずり込んで、思ってもみないような時にバン！　だ"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1059
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_95120565:

    # hi "Bam what?"
    hi "何をバン？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1061
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_aa004feb:

    # "Kenji seems slightly fazed at my skepticism, but not any less loony."
    "健二はその質問にやや動じたみたいだけど、やつの狂気はおさまらない。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1066
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_4af4bc8b:

    # ke "It doesn't matter."
    ke "どうでもいいだろ"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1068
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_14ab0100:

    # ke "Tread carefully man, tread carefully."
    ke "慎重にいけよ、慎重にな"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1079
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_2237351f:

    # "The happy hubbub of the crowd greets me as I push myself through the main door and step outside."
    "体を押すように正面のドアを抜け外に出ると、陽気な喧騒が俺を迎える。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1081
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_bde7293a:

    # "The school grounds were transformed into festival grounds over yesterday and this morning."
    "昨日から今朝までのあいだに、学校の敷地はお祭り会場へと様変わりしていた。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1083
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_782ed8c1:

    # "Colorful stands line at the main walkways from the main entrance to the school building."
    "正門から校舎にかけての通りにはカラフルな屋台が並んでいる。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1085
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_3585677f:

    # "Some people are still carrying stuff to and fro, but behind most counters are relaxed students who look like they are good to go."
    "何人かはまだ色々なものを運んで行ったり来たりしているけど、それ以外のほとんどはリラックスしてカウンターにつき、準備が整っているようだ。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1087
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_bb22f75d:

    # "Most of the other students have been up early to finish the preparations."
    "今ゆっくりしている生徒たちは、早起きして準備を終わらせていたんだろう。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1089
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_3f84924b:

    # "A feeling of guilt passes through me, but it soon goes away."
    "自分は何もしていないことに悪い気がしたが、すぐに思い直した。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1091
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_ea90b342:

    # "I'm just a lowly transfer student, after all."
    "なんだかんだで、俺はしがない新入りなのだから。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1093
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_5b981ef3:

    # "Some visitors are already strolling around the grounds."
    "すでに外からのお客が学園内を散策している。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1095
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_1bfed8cb:

    # "There are some young families with the perturbed parents trying to keep up with their overenthusiastic offspring…"
    "はしゃぎまくる子供を心配げに追いかける、そんな若い家族がいて……"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1097
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_b0c80f37:

    # "…a few students of our own accompanied by their parents…"
    "……生徒の中にも両親と一緒の人がいて……"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1099
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_89c5850e:

    # "…and a lot of old and young people who are here for no reason I can imagine."
    "……そして老若男女さまざまな人々が、理由はわからないがここにいる。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1103
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_8604e465:

    # "The carillon bursts into life and the principal's squeaky voice announces the opening of the festival over the PA system."
    "カリヨンが鳴り、学長の甲高い声が拡声器から雑音混じりに学園祭の幕開けを告げる。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1105
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_e3987c45:

    # "Everyone applauds politely if a bit unenthusiastically."
    "みんな乗り気ではなさそうだけど、それでも律儀に拍手を返す。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1107
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_06eeaeea:

    # "A school festival… we didn't really have festivals at my old high school. It feels kind of old-fashioned, especially considering the school I came from, but it's still somewhat exciting."
    "学園祭……前の学校には祭らしい行事はまったくなかった。その事を考えると特に、祭なんて古臭い気がする。とはいえ、祭には不思議な高揚感がある。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1109
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_f2c584c5:

    # "A day off feels sweet after the first week of hard work, despite me lying on the hospital bed for four months prior to this."
    "4ヶ月間もずっとベッドで寝て過ごしていたとはいえ、忙しく過ごしたこの一週間の後に、休日とは実にありがたいものだ。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1111
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_12d9127a:

    # "I recall even wishing that I could go to math lessons during my stint at the hospital."
    "俺は病院にいる間、数学の授業にでも出られればと思っていたのを思い出す。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1113
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_29b2d665:

    # "I can't remember the program for the festival, even though Mutou went through it during class just the other day."
    "ついこの間先生が説明してくれたのに、学園祭のプログラムを忘れてしまった。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1115
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_e49d7ca4:

    # "I step off the dorm steps, intending to take a tour around the grounds to see all the stuff the others have set up, but I only make it down to the bottom of the stairs."
    "俺も他のクラスの出し物を見ながら辺りを散策しようと思い、寮の階段を降りていく。しかし、俺は階段の下に目をとめる。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1123
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_99e7a6bd:

    # "A few people are studying Rin's mural on the wall, while the artist herself is lounging on the sidelines, leaning against the wall and looking extremely bored and mildly under the weather."
    "何人かの人が琳の壁画を見物している。その制作者は脇で壁にもたれかかってくつろいでいる。とても退屈そうで、少し元気がなさそうに見える。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1125
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_8e4a18dc:

    # hi "Good morning."
    hi "おはよう"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1130
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_811c5f41:

    # rin "Hello."
    rin "やあ"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1132
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_bc12ad1a:

    # hi "How's it going?"
    hi "調子はどうだ？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1137
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_1fa4ae12:

    # rin "Nowhere."
    rin "ん、別に"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1139
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_f2a6f01e:

    # rin "I'm stuck."
    rin "動けなくて"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1141
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_8599cac7:

    # hi "What do you mean stuck?"
    hi "動けないって？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1143
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_1f515898:

    # rin "I mean I can't walk stuck. I think my legs are out of order because of yesterday."
    rin "歩けないの。昨日のせいで足が言うこと聞かなくてさ"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1145
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_5ae54e10:

    # hi "Does it hurt?"
    hi "痛むのか？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1150
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_463926d2:

    # rin "It's hard to say. Maybe."
    rin "わかんない、たぶん"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1152
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_9540ae19:

    # "The strain of working on the mural was greater than she let me know. I thought it was just a bit of tired muscles or something. I mean to ask something further, but Rin swiftly moves on to another topic."
    "壁画の作業は琳が言っている以上に大きな負担だったんだろう。俺はてっきり、ただの筋肉痛だと思っていた。もっと詳しく聞こうと思ったけど、琳はすぐに話題を切り替えてしまう。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1157
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_714846d2:

    # rin "Teacher's friends came by."
    rin "先生のお友達、来たよ"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1162
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_9e265ab4:

    # rin "Then they headed into town for lunch and asked me to go. It was a good thing my legs hurt so much."
    rin "そんで町に下りていったよ、お昼食べに。私も誘われたけど。足が痛くてよかった"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1164
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_d4d5fe8f:

    # hi "But you're stuck sitting there? That's not good."
    hi "でも、動けなくてここに座ってるんだろ？　どこも良くないじゃないか"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1169
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_ce5dc46e:

    # rin "I'll just wait till I can walk again. It should be either sooner or later, if you think about it for a while."
    rin "歩けるようになるまで待つよ。考えてみれば、そのうち治るはずだよね"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1171
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_5f72eee7:

    # rin "Teacher was happy that I finished the mural."
    rin "先生、私がちゃんと描き終えてて嬉しそうだった"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1173
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_d6a9168e:

    # hi "He should be."
    hi "そりゃそうだろう"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1180
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_1bfe5c98:

    # rin "But I wonder if it's finished after all."
    rin "でも、本当にこれ、完成してるのかなあって"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1182
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_f9075882:

    # hi "Oh?"
    hi "ほう？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1187
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_cb4e2947:

    # rin "I thought yesterday that I had done everything, but now I'm not sure any more. I should paint more details. Maybe. Probably. It's very hard to decide."
    rin "昨日、全部描き終わったと思ったんだ。でも今見るとなんだか自信持てなくて。もっと細かいところ描かないと。多分、きっと。どこで終わりにするか決めるのって難しいんだ"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1189
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_ccf9b6c4:

    # "Finished or not, the mural looks great in broad daylight."
    "未完成だったとしても、この白日の下では実にすばらしいものに見えるけど。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1197
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_3ef7eba0:

    # "Various human body parts, repeated over and over in a wildly mutating, mostly disfigured variety are the main element."
    "主に絵を構成しているのは、何度も何度も繰り返し描かれている、人間のさまざまなパーツだ。どれも著しく奇妙な形で、そしてほとんどが醜く変貌している。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1199
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_04fb1181:

    # "They are rough-looking, as if thoughtlessly placed and rudimentarily painted, but a great deal of thought and care has gone into each and every one of them."
    "一見、粗く見える。構図は適当で、塗り方もごく基本的なように見える。だけど、一つ一つのパーツに念入りな考慮と注意が注がれている。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1205
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_578c6b52:

    # hi "Does this one have a frog growing out of his head?"
    hi "これは頭から蛙が伸びてるのか？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1207
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_e2f71bbe:

    # rin "It's a goldfish."
    rin "それ、金魚"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1213
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_111a58e1:

    # hi "What's that?"
    hi "これは？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1215
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_c3862712:

    # rin "It's nothing."
    rin "なんでもない"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1220
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_c5873921:

    # "Anyway…"
    "それにしても……"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1222
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_c83b9405:

    # "The wall is so wide I have to turn my neck from side to side to see the entire painting."
    "この壁は幅が広く、壁画全体を見渡すには首を動かし回さないといけない。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1224
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_b6f63161:

    # "It's hard to consider it as a single piece. The elements don't seem to fit together, but I guess they do create some kind of a whole."
    "一枚の絵としては考えるのは難しい。描かれているものはそれぞれ噛み合っているようには見えないからだ。でも、それらがある種全体像を構成している。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1226
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_d6cc8c33:

    # "Abstract as it is, I have no idea what it's supposed to be portraying, but it looks nice. That's enough for me."
    "抽象的すぎて何を表現しているのかまるでわからない。でもいい絵だ。それだけでも十分だ。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1228
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_4c3c0e2c:

    # "I settle myself next to Rin, leaning against the wall like she does."
    "俺は琳の隣に腰を下ろし、同じように壁にもたれかかる。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1230
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_95d06112:

    # "The happy noises of the festival are becoming louder as more and more folks enter the grounds."
    "次々と来客が校内に入ってきて、学園祭の陽気な騒がしさは大きくなる一方だ。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1232
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_404677c0:

    # "The dorms are far from the main attractions in the main building and the stands around the courtyard, so most visitors have not found their way here yet."
    "多くの出し物が集まる本館や中庭の周囲にある屋台から寮は離れているため、ここに人はあまり来ていない。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1242
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_65287e9e:

    # "A somewhat bored expression settles on Rin's face, making her look detached from everything that's going around her."
    "琳の表情に退屈が表れ始めている。まるで琳が周囲の喧騒から隔てられているかのように。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1244
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_f74711a8:

    # "She is being awfully quiet. I wonder if she's in pain."
    "彼女はずっと黙ったままだ。まだ痛むのだろうか？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1246
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_092ffe2f:

    # hi "So what did the art people say about your mural?"
    hi "それで、先生のお友達ってのは壁画のこと、なんて言ってた？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1251
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_2b00e258:

    # "My question wakes Rin from her daydreaming. She lazily turns her face towards me."
    "俺が問いかけると、琳は白昼夢から我に返る。けだるそうに顔をこっちに向ける。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1256
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_0efef7a5:

    # rin "I'm not sure."
    rin "よくわからない"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1261
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_e0889731:

    # rin "I think they liked it? Maybe they did."
    rin "気に入ってたのかな？　ホントに気に入ってたのかもね"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1263
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_7bd025d1:

    # hi "What about you? Are you happy with the mural? 'Cause I kind of participated, it'd be terrible if you were unhappy."
    hi "お前はどうなんだ？　絵には満足してるのか？　俺も手伝いみたいなことはしたからさ。お前が嬉しくないってのも嫌だぞ"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1265
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_49f5fa46:

    # "Rin tilts her head, biting her lower lip."
    "琳は下唇を噛み、首を傾げる。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1270
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_0511ed59:

    # rin "I think it came out decently. It's not bad but it's not good either. It just… is. I guess I'm all right at being empty-minded."
    rin "ちゃんと出来てはいると思うよ。良くも悪くもない感じ。ただ……それだけかな。きっと、うまく何も考えずにいられたんだろうね"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1272
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_8e6bca21:

    # hi "Can I ask something else? What does the painting really portray? I thought about it yesterday, when you said that it doesn't portray anything."
    hi "もう一つ訊いていいか？　これは本当は何を表現してるんだ？　昨日、考えてたんだ。お前が、何も表現してない、なんて言ってたとき"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1274
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_5eb22096:

    # hi "But that's a logical fallacy, isn't it? You can't make something out of nothing, not even art."
    hi "でもそんなんじゃ理屈に合わないだろ？　何も考えないでものを作るなんてできるはずない、美術だってそうだ"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1279
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_e97414a2:

    # "Rin frowns and turns her head back towards the clouds."
    "琳はしかめ面をして雲を仰ぐ。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1281
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_ca495d5a:

    # rin "I don't know. I am not really good at explaining things. It's just a mural; there is nothing special to it. I said it already."
    rin "知らないよ。私は説明するの得意じゃないんだ。これはただの壁画。特別なことなんて何もないよ。前も言ったよね"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1283
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_9bfececf:

    # "She sounds annoyed at my inquiries."
    "俺の質問にイラついているようだ。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1285
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_43491111:

    # rin "I didn't know what I'd paint, so I decided to paint just a mural."
    rin "自分で何を描きたいかわからなかった。だからただの壁画を描いたの"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1287
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_283fde58:

    # rin "It's a mural that portrays a mural."
    rin "これは壁画を表した壁画ってわけ"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1292
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_25e35b54:

    # rin "No, wait. I just thought up a better way to say it: It portrays itself."
    rin "待って、いい言い方が見つかった。これは『自分で自分を表現してる』んだよ"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1297
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_7581d85c:

    # rin "So… its muralness is at the maximum, at least as far as I can do, so if you think it has some meaning, I think that's the same as this one has."
    rin "だから……この絵は最高に壁画らしいんだ。少なくとも私のできる範囲では。君がこの絵に他に何か意味があるって言うなら、それもそうなんじゃない"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1299
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_8c6f9d56:

    # "That makes no sense."
    "何を言っているんだ。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1301
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_bbbda5c0:

    # "Meaning… I feel the corners of my mouth turning upwards into a smile that's just a tiny bit bothered."
    "他の意味……自分の口角が上がって、少し困ったような笑顔になっていくのを感じる。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1308
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_4bba9043:

    # "I have never understood art in the deepest meaning of the word."
    "俺は『美術』という言葉を本当に深い意味で理解したことはなかった。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1310
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_d2bd2e19:

    # "I get the basics, how art is supposed to be only a means for exchanging ideas and thoughts."
    "美術は発想や思考をやりとりする手段でしかない、という基本的なことはわかる。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1317
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_58a65e6a:

    # "However, I never learned how I should interpret a piece of art, to somehow divine what the artist intends to say through it."
    "でも、美術作品をどう理解すべきか、作り手の主張をどうやって推し測ればいいのか、そんなことを学んだことは一度もなかった。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1319
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_c669a675:

    # "I know it's not any special skill, but somehow, my brain never can connect art with anything else than what I see. All I see is a mural."
    "別にそれが特別な技術じゃないことはわかってる。でもどういうわけか、俺の脳は美術作品を目に見えるもの以外のことと関連づけることができない。俺の目に見えるのはただの壁画だけだ。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1321
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_77d1b81c:

    # "I can admire the technical skill, after all even I know the difference between bad art and mediocre art; mediocre art and good art."
    "そんな技能があれば尊敬する。たしかに、俺でも悪い作品とそれなりの作品、それなりの作品と良い作品の違いぐらいならわかる。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1323
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_4642f504:

    # "But that's as far as I can go, so don't ask me about meanings, Rin."
    "でも俺にできるのはそこまでだ。だから俺にこの作品の意図を求めないでくれ、琳。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1325
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_2a79affd:

    # "Her reply sure made me reluctant to ask her about it any further either."
    "琳の答えのおかげで、俺もこれ以上絵のことを聞くのをためらってしまう。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1327
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_b3a7992b:

    # hi "So what are you doing when you get on your feet?"
    hi "ところで、歩けるようになったらどうするんだ？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1336
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_be162ee9:

    # rin "Nothing."
    rin "何もいらない"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1338
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_bffeb373:

    # hi "Nothing? But there's the festival, don't you want to go have some fun?"
    hi "何もしないのか？　せっかくの学園祭なのに、遊びにいかないのか？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1343
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_dfb2cc52:

    # rin "I'm fine like this."
    rin "このままでいい"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1345
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_deb0546f:

    # hi "You don't like socializing much, do you?"
    hi "あんまり人付き合いは好きじゃないんだろ、違うか？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1347
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_9832b19f:

    # "I think I'm arguing more for her than for myself at this point. It's not that I'm particularly thrilled about the festival, either; just a bit curious to see what it's like, and that's about it."
    "自分に言っているような気がした。俺自身、取り立てて言うほど学園祭を楽しんでいない。ちょっとどんな様子かと気になっているだけだ。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1349
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_f37ddd5e:

    # "Her answer is unsurprising."
    "琳の答えは予想通りだった。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1354
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_7099ab01:

    # rin "No, I don't."
    rin "そうだよ"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1356
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_96ebbd81:

    # hi "I guess… me neither, in the end."
    hi "俺もそうみたいだけどな"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1361
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_4210c18b:

    # rin "You should go if you want to."
    rin "行きたかったら行っていいよ"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1363
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_66a302ce:

    # hi "I know, but I can keep you company. I'm not used to all this just yet, so it's okay to take it easy."
    hi "わかってる。でもお前に付き合うよ。俺もまだこういうことには慣れてないし、気楽にしてて問題ないさ"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1365
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_1939e750:

    # hi "I can leave though, if you want to be alone."
    hi "まあ一人になりたいって言うなら、もう行くけど"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1370
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_7a514f37:

    # rin "I like it if you are here."
    rin "ここにいてくれないかな"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1372
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_df5be72b:

    # "We circle around each other with words, but eventually end up somewhere. Her saying that makes me feel oddly happy, so I stay."
    "言葉でぐるぐる巻きになるようなやり取りが、ようやく落ち着いた。琳がそう言ってくれたことに妙に嬉しくなってここに残る。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1374
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_7d67d66b:

    # "Her presence is something I like too. The odd, warm aura of serenity that she seems to emanate makes it comfortable to be silent. I really like that."
    "俺も琳がそばにいると気分がいい。琳の持つ奇妙な、でも暖かい静かな雰囲気は沈黙も心地よいものにしてくれる。俺はそれが本当に気に入っている。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1376
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_25b3a15e:

    # "We watch people walk by, the two of us silent, everyone else chattering happily among themselves."
    "俺たちは行きかう人々を眺める。俺たちは沈黙し、ほかの人達は楽しそうにお喋りをしている。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1378
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_63a61469:

    # "Students are leading their families to the dorms to show their rooms. They pass us and the mural, maybe glance at it once or twice."
    "生徒たちが自室を見せるために家族を連れている。俺たちとその後ろの壁画の横を通り過ぎる。壁画をちらちらと何度か見ていたかも知れない。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1380
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_53b648ba:

    # "I pay less attention to them, and more to my companion, trying to figure my way past her cryptic, unreadable wall of a face."
    "俺は彼らから隣の連れ合いに注意を移して、謎めいた読めない表情の奥にあるものを見つけようとする。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1391
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_ae9f43f8:

    # "Rin's eyes flicker restlessly from one person to another as they walk by."
    "琳の眼は通りすがる人々を追ってせわしなく動く。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1393
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_434af3dc:

    # "Is she waiting for people to stop at the mural, maybe secretly hoping someone would comment on it?"
    "誰かが壁画を前に足を止めてくれるのを待っているのだろうか。まさか密かに感想を聞けることに期待してるのだろうか？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1395
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_536f28c7:

    # "I don't think anyone would assume she was the artist. We're just sitting here like a pair of hobos, after all, and she doesn't even have hands."
    "誰も、この絵を描いたのが琳だなんては思わないだろう。俺たちはこうして浮浪者のように座り込んでいるだけなんだから。それに、琳には腕がない。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1397
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_92195435:

    # "I wonder if it's even in Rin's style to fish for compliments. She seems so aloof."
    "ひょっとしたら、これが琳なりのアピールなんだろうか。そっけないものだ。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1399
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_edb5986a:

    # "More people walk by, some of them pointing their fingers at the mural, exchanging words that I can't make out. Someone drops a snow cone on his shoe. Too bad for him."
    "さらに多くの人が通り、ときには壁画を指差し何かを話すけど聞き取れない。誰かがつま先にかき氷をこぼした。お気の毒に。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1401
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_00db9a8d:

    # hi "Everyone seems to like it."
    hi "みんな気に入ってるみたいだな"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1403
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_6b06d794:

    # "I suggest it tentatively, throwing a topic in the stale summer air separating us."
    "空気がダレてきたところで、何か話題にと思ってそう言ってみる。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1405
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_e34402c1:

    # "Rin doesn't answer right away, but by now I am mostly used to her occasional slowness when she must talk. It's like she takes great care picking her words, which is really unbelievable when you consider the jumble that comes out of her mouth."
    "琳はすぐには返事をしない。でも必要に迫られて琳が口を開く時に、ときどき反応が遅くなるのにはもう慣れている。 まるで琳が慎重に言葉を選んでいるかのようだけど、実際に出てくる言葉が意味不明なことを考えると、とてもそうは思えない。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1410
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_7cac8d6d:

    # rin "I wanted to make it so that you can just look at it without thinking. Then I realized that it doesn't make any sense. So it became something like a mix of this and that."
    rin "何も考えずに見ることのできる絵にしたかったんだ。でもそんなのナンセンスだって気づいたから、あれこれ混ぜこんだような絵になったわけ"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1415
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_89cd3f4a:

    # rin "From far away, it looks like someone vomited a herd of butterflies on the wall. Which is exactly what that obnoxious president person didn't want. Is that word that?"
    rin "遠くから見るとさ、誰かが蝶の群れを吐きつけたような絵だよ。いじわるな生徒会長さんは嫌がるだろうね……そういう言い方でいいのかな？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1417
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_a0a32ac5:

    # hi "What word?"
    hi "言い方？　何の？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1422
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_b4bf3d86:

    # rin "That. What is the word for more than one butterfly?"
    rin "だからそういう。一羽以上の蝶って他に言い方ある？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1424
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_d44cf8a0:

    # hi "Butterflies?"
    hi "蝶？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1429
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_89744c4d:

    # rin "No, like a herd, or a school, or a heap."
    rin "じゃなくて。『群れ』とか『集まり』とか『大量』とか"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1431
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_316b5411:

    # hi "Oh. I don't know. A flock maybe?"
    hi "ああ……さぁね。『大群』とか？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1433
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_458a5aa8:

    # rin "Maybe people like butterfly vomit."
    rin "きっと人って蝶みたいに集まるんだね"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1438
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_99b8585a:

    # "Rin looks at the mural, looking surprisingly unhappy."
    "琳は驚くほど不満そうに壁画を見る。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1440
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_28b06d38:

    # rin "The middle could be better."
    rin "真ん中の辺り、もう少し何とかならないかなあ"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1445
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_cbda0905:

    # rin "Usually I like in-betweens, but this was a pain in my butt. Not literally of course… then again I did get that too. I guess it was literally after all."
    rin "いつもは中間色が好きなんだけど、これはお尻が痛むなあ。いや、そのままの意味じゃないけど……でもほんとに痛くなっちゃったんだよね。やっぱりそのままの意味だったみたい"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1447
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_8ef1412b:

    # hi "Don't be so critical of yourself."
    hi "そう自分を悪く言うなよ"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1452
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_390228e2:

    # "She looks at me funnily, but shuts up."
    "琳はおもしろおかしそうに俺を見るけど、話すのはやめる。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1457
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_b22f25f8:

    # "At about this point I start thinking if I should really leave and do something more constructive with my Sunday."
    "この辺で、俺はここを立ち去って、もっと建設的な日曜を過ごしたほうがいいんじゃないか、と考え始める。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1459
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_b3f218ab:

    # "This is the pinnacle of social failure. A whole free day, a festival right outside my doorstep, and what do I do?"
    "これじゃ社会不適合の極みだ。丸一日フリーで、目と鼻の先では学園祭をやってて、それで俺は何をしてるんだ？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1461
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_6233b155:

    # "Sit here with Rin; two bystanders with nothing to do except to think what a pity it is to be just a bystander."
    "琳とこの場にいる……２人の見物人が、ただの見物人であることを嘆く以外にすることもなくこの場にいる。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1463
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_0bf31dbf:

    # "Even realizing how pitiful it is, I don't do anything. I don't stand up and take off for a day of fun."
    "そのみじめさを理解しながらも、俺は何もしない。楽しい一日のために立ち上がりも、歩き出しもしない。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1469
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_28a1ecf7:

    # centered "*shuffle shuffle*"
    centered "*ごそごそ　もぞもぞ*"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1471
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_ce617998:

    # "…"
    "……"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1473
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_dac04043:

    # centered "*fidget*"
    centered "*もじもじ*"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1477
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_016bc641:

    # centered "*shuffle*"
    centered "*ごそごそ*"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1479
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_ce617998_1:

    # "…"
    "……"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1486
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_ef4fcbde:

    # "Rin is shuffling about restlessly, constantly swinging one leg over the other knee and then back again."
    "琳は落ち着きなく体をもぞもぞと動かす。片方の足をもう片方の膝の上で、休みなく揺らしている。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1488
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_6e818307:

    # "She has a very irritated look on her face."
    "とても苛立った表情が顔に浮かんでいる。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1490
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_9dbd43ff:

    # hi "Is something wrong?"
    hi "なんかおかしい？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1495
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_99dbf985:

    # rin "Yes. No. Yes."
    rin "ん、別に。うん"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1506
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_05dff07c:

    # "She suddenly hops up on her feet. It's surprising, I thought she was still rendered immobile but apparently that's not the case."
    "琳は突然飛び上がる。驚いた、まだ動けないのかと思っていたけど、どうやらそうでもなかったようだ。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1511
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_8296e7d5:

    # rin "I have to go find Emi or someone, I need some help with something."
    rin "笑美か誰か探してこないと。ちょっと手伝って欲しいことがあるんだ"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1513
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_0f9db7e3:

    # hi "I can help you."
    hi "俺が手伝うよ"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1518
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_5ad1fd34:

    # rin "No, it's okay. One of us has to stay here in case something happens."
    rin "ん、いいよ。何かあるといけないから、一人はここにいないと"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1520
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_225c8a47:

    # hi "Don't be ridiculous. Nothing even remotely interesting has happened since I came here except that one guy who dropped a snow cone on his foot. Let me help you, since I'm bored."
    hi "馬鹿なこと言うなよ。俺が来てからずっと面白いこと１つなかったじゃないか、かき氷を落っことしたやつがいただけ。だから手伝わせてくれよ、俺も暇なんだ"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1522
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_817d42f0:

    # hi "So what is it?"
    hi "それで、なんなんだ？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1527
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_e8e1bffb:

    # "Rin's lips flatten tightly against each other into an almost perfectly horizontal line."
    "琳の唇が水平線のように平たく閉じられる。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1532
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_c6cc1295:

    # "She closes her eyes and draws in a deep breath."
    "そして目をつむり、深く息をつく。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1534
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_43fa29db:

    # "When she opens her eyelids the frighteningly stern look in her dark eyes takes me aback."
    "再び開かれたその目は、恐ろしいほど険しく、俺は面食らってしまう。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1541
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_378f4709:

    # rin "Hisao, you might not want to hear this or maybe you do, I don't know, but it doesn't matter and even if it did you are not leaving me any choice."
    rin "久夫……君がこんなこと聞きたいかどうかはわからないけど、でも関係ない、聞きたくなかったとしても君のせいだからね"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1543
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_059a6012:

    # rin "I'm having my period and I need some help regarding that. However, I don't feel that our relationship is yet on the level where I could allow you to pull my underwear down in the girls' toilet even if you offer to."
    rin "生理が来たからそれで手伝いが欲しいの。でも君と私は、まだ女子トイレまでご一緒して下着を下ろしてもらうほどの仲じゃないと思うんだ。君が手伝うと言ってくれてもね"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1545
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_015c44fe:

    # rin "That's why you should stay here while I go and look for Emi."
    rin "そういうわけだから、君にここにいてもらって、私は笑美を探しにいきたいの"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1547
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_aa06572a:

    # "As blood rushes to my cheeks like the rising tide my brains try to desperately search for an answer, but the only thing I can think of is how that was the most coherent thing I have heard coming out of Rin's mouth during these four days I've known her."
    "上昇気流のように、俺の頬に血が上りつめて来ながらも、俺は必死に答えを返そうとした。 でも俺の頭に浮かんだのは、出会ってからの４日間、琳の口から聞いた言葉の中で、今のが一番わかりやすかったな、ということだけだった。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1549
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_b3d21ad1:

    # hi "Yes."
    hi "ぜひ聞きたい"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1556
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_b9969234:

    # "Not wanting to meet Rin's eyes, I turn my face aside, pretending I'm looking at someone's parents."
    "俺は琳と目を合わせないように、誰かの親を見ているふりをして顔をそむける。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1558
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_97881b99:

    # "From the corner of my eye I see Rin turning on her heel and walking off without further ado."
    "視界の隅に、琳がさっさと振り向いて去っていくのが見えた。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1560
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_2f34d0a4:

    # "I feel like going to hide under some rock."
    "穴があったら入りたい気分だ。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1562
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_f3e47f99:

    # "I wonder how long Rin will be gone… or if she will return at all."
    "琳はいつ帰ってくるだろう……もう戻ってこないんじゃないだろうか。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1570
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_8adbd84e:

    # "She does return eventually, appearing seemingly out of nowhere and sitting back to where she was, next to my place."
    "やがて琳はどこからともなく戻ってくると、俺の横の、元いたところに腰を下ろす。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1579
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_81387027:

    # rin "I'm back."
    rin "ただいま"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1581
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_8ab5ee79:

    # "She says it flatly, like my blunder never happened. I'd prefer to forget the whole matter as well, so I keep quiet."
    "こともなげに言う。俺の失態などなかったかのように。俺も早く忘れてしまいたかったので、口をつぐんでおく。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1592
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_38aade8b:

    # "Time passes in standstill, the sun gleams from high above the main building. It hits me directly in the eyes, but I just squint instead of moving."
    "時間がゆっくりと過ぎていく。日の光が本校舎の向こうから洩れ、俺の目に直に降り注ぐ。だけど俺はその場から動かず、目を細めるだけだ。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1594
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_53893ddc:

    # "In a bit it becomes painful to keep my eyes open just a little, and my temples start aching."
    "間もなく、目をわずかに開けているのも辛くなってくる。こめかみが痛み始める。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1596
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_6050e6a3:

    # hi "My head hurts. I think this day gave me a headache, can you believe it?"
    hi "頭が痛くなってきた。今日は頭が痛くなる日だ。そういうのってあると思うか？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1601
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_4a289d99:

    # rin "Are you hungry?"
    rin "お腹でも空いたの？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1603
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_da0dcc4d:

    # hi "How is that related to headache?"
    hi "頭痛とは関係ないだろ？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1608
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_3c820e2d:

    # rin "It's not. I ask because I am."
    rin "そうだね。私がお腹空いたから訊いてみたの"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1610
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_ce617998_2:

    # "…"
    "……"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1612
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_c19bc68f:

    # "Her oblivious seriousness melts my irritation with its ridiculousness, and I find the corners of my mouth turning slightly upwards again."
    "琳のノーテンキさの前では、俺の苛立ちも馬鹿馬鹿しく思える。そしていつの間にか口元も緩んでいる。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1614
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_cdbaf061:

    # hi "You know what? So am I."
    hi "実は俺もそうだ"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1616
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_fdd18b35:

    # hi "I'll go get some food for us. What do you want? My treat."
    hi "何か食べる物でも買ってくるよ。何がいい？　おごるよ"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1621
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_764a7cab:

    # rin "Doesn't matter."
    rin "なんでもいいよ"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1626
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_844b6bf3:

    # "Returning with the food, I give one portion to Rin, taking the other for myself and we dig in without a word."
    "食べ物を調達して戻り、一人分を琳に渡す。残りは俺の分だ。俺たちは言葉も交わさず食事に専念する。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1633
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_9ab26115:

    # "Rin looks upwards, fork hanging out the corner of her mouth."
    "琳は口元にフォークをぶら下げたまま、上を見上げる。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1635
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_0c569ed0:

    # rin "What are clouds? I always thought they were thoughts of the sky or something like that. Because you can't touch them."
    rin "雲ってなんだろね？　私、雲って空の思考なんじゃないかっていつも思ってた。だって、直接さわれないし"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1637
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_cf648604:

    # hi "You thought like that when you were a kid?"
    hi "子供のころにそう思ってたのか？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1639
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_3ea52055:

    # rin "No, last week."
    rin "ううん、先週の話"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1641
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_8a99da96:

    # rin "Maybe because sometimes my thoughts feel like clouds. Fluffy and white and slow."
    rin "たぶん私の思考が時々雲に似てる感じだからじゃない？　もこもこで、白くて、ゆーっくりでさ"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1643
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_d2c8744c:

    # rin "Like the sky was in my mind. Like my mind was the sky."
    rin "私の心に空が広がってるみたいに。私の心が空そのものみたいに"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1645
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_3ddfb1b0:

    # hi "The sky of your mind?"
    hi "心の空？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1647
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_7ac509bd:

    # rin "Close your eyes and think of sky. You won't be able to think of anything else until you stop."
    rin "目を閉じて空のことを考えてみなよ。他のことなんか考えられなくなるよ"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1652
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_6da813a7:

    # "I try it. It works. Magic?"
    "やってみた。確かにそうなった。これは魔法か？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1661
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_cabccb40:

    # "Opening my eyes, I see Rin studying me with her eyes. It feels uncomfortable because she doesn't say anything. I turn away."
    "目を開けると、琳は俺をしげしげと眺めている。その間、琳が何も言わないのが気になり、俺はそっぽを向く。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1668
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_8b98ba66:

    # hi "Clouds are water. Evaporated water."
    hi "雲は水分だ。蒸発した水"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1670
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_1a2614d0:

    # hi "You know they say that almost all of the water in the world will at some point of its existence be a part of a cloud."
    hi "地球上のほとんどの水は、いつかは蒸発して雲の一部になるんだろ"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1672
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_483375f1:

    # hi "Every drop of tears and blood and sweat that comes out of you, it'll be a cloud. All the water inside your body too, it goes up there some time after you die. It might take a while though."
    hi "お前から出た汗や涙、血も雲になるんだ。体のほかの水分もみんな。お前が死んだ後もいつかはそうなる。時間はかかるかもしれないけどな"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1674
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_779356c4:

    # rin "Your explanation is better than any of mine."
    rin "私より説明、上手だね"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1676
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_2872339c:

    # hi "Because it's true."
    hi "事実だからな"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1678
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_4449f288:

    # rin "That must be it."
    rin "違いないね"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1680
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_b5ddaa5e:

    # "I carry on eating the food before it gets cold."
    "俺は食事が冷めないうちに食べ続ける。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1682
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_2ce67ac9:

    # "The wall offers a bit of blessed shade as the sun revolves around the dome of the sky."
    "太陽が寮の上空をまたぎ、壁に煌びやかな影が落ちる。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1684
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_c7b417d1:

    # "But the afternoon is already slowly making way for the evening so our lunch becomes more of a dinner. Or whatever the word is for an irregular meal like this."
    "だけど、午後という時間はすでに夕方に差し掛かかり、俺たちの昼飯は夕飯になりつつある。待てよ、こういう時間にとる食事はなんて言えばいいんだ？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1686
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_a76c28c2:

    # "Despite what I decide to call it, it certainly hits the spot. I haven't eaten a bit since forever."
    "そうこう考えている間にも、食欲は満たされていく。もう長いこと何も口にしていなかった。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1688
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_ce617998_3:

    # "…"
    "……"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1690
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_14d89a4f:

    # "My appetite filled, I let out a satisfied sigh. Rin hasn't eaten all of hers but seems to be done with her food as well."
    "すっかり食べ終えると、俺は満足げにため息をつく。一方、琳はまだ食べ終えていないけど、もう満腹のようだ。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1692
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_373b030d:

    # "I lean back, taking in the atmosphere. The crowd has thinned already, but the activities are still going. Everyone seems to be enjoying themselves."
    "壁にもたれかかり、息を吸い込む。見物人はまばらになってきていたけど、学園祭はまだ続いている。みんなそれぞれ楽しんでいるようだ。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1694
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_10667acd:

    # "And why not? It's warm, the kind of perfect summer day when it's hot but not too hot for comfort."
    "そりゃ楽しまない理由がない。今日は暑いけど、快適でいられないほど暑すぎはしない。暖かくて、完璧な夏の日と言える。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1696
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_edbbbffd:

    # "The sun will set soon. Time really has flown by."
    "もうすぐ日が落ちる。時間の流れが速かったな。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1705
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_9d5936f9:

    # hi "We've been sitting here for six hours."
    hi "もうかれこれ６時間はここに座ってるな"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1710
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_44a5811a:

    # rin "Yes we have."
    rin "そうだね"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1715
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_56ef8943:

    # rin "Do you want to do something else now?"
    rin "他にしたいことないの？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1717
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_21ad072c:

    # hi "No, not really."
    hi "いや、別に"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1722
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_6b57485c:

    # rin "Me neither."
    rin "私も"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1727
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_930e7af7:

    # "She adjusts her position and leans against the wall, and I follow her lead, relaxing my own body."
    "琳は姿勢を直して壁に寄りかかる。俺もそれにならって、体をくつろがせる。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1729
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_6e28168e:

    # "For minutes on end, we sit there without saying a word."
    "それからの数分間、俺たちは会話もなしにそこに座り続けた。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1731
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_8189fa3f:

    # "I'm trying to feel Rin's mood from her demeanor, the tension of her muscles, the tiny expressions fleeting on her face. It's no use. She's unreadable as always."
    "琳が今どんな気分か感じ取ろうと、琳の様子や、体の緊張具合や、顔に浮かぶ僅かな表情に注意する。無駄なことだった。いつもながらに内心が読めない。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1740
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_ea5b2aff:

    # "The crowd swells to and fro, people happily chattering with each other. Very few people pay real attention to the mural, and even less to us."
    "行き交う人が増えていく。みんな楽しそうに言葉を交わしている。本当に壁画に注目する人は少ない。俺たちに目を向ける人はもっと少ない。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1742
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_1d7d3431:

    # "I fiddle with a few odd pebbles absentmindedly."
    "俺はぼんやりと道端の小石をいじる。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1744
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_fc284cfd:

    # "The act of doing something just for the sake of doing something, the pinnacle of idleness."
    "何かすること自体を目的に何かをするなんて、怠惰もいいところだ。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1746
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_d879d465:

    # "Inch by inch, the sun creeps lower and lower towards the treeline, changing the color of the sky close to the horizon from golden yellow to orange and red as the moment of sunset draws near."
    "次第に太陽は、空を水平線近くから黄金やオレンジ、赤に染めながら、並木の向こうに落ちていく。日没も近い。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1748
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_f2b63416:

    # "I feel like my stomach is filled with lead after eating so heavily, but the brick wall feels surprisingly comfortable against my back."
    "食べ過ぎて腹の中に鉛が詰まっているみたいだ。でもレンガの壁に寄りかかると驚くほど気分が良い。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1750
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_30cd01cc:

    # "I try to fight against the drowsy feeling that is overwhelming me, to no avail."
    "強い眠気に抗おうとするけど、耐えきれない。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1766
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_a8cec96f:

    # "I wake up with a start."
    "俺はハッとして目を覚ます。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1768
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_4f8e1ea1:

    # "A low boom reverberates through the school grounds. Afterimages of bright sparks flash through my vision like stars."
    "低い轟音が学園中に響きわたっている。輝く火花の残像が星のように視界を駆ける。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1770
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_803f9919:

    # "Something rises towards the skies from the direction of the sports field."
    "運動場のほうから何かが空に昇っていく。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1772
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_49f862d9:

    # "A tail of fire trails behind it until a burst of red and yellow flame lights the sky high above the school with another loud boom."
    "炎が尾を引き、轟音とともに弾け、赤や黄色が学校上空を照らす。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1777
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_dc1b0b5e:

    # "Fireworks."
    "花火だ。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1779
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_4ce65611:

    # "The sudden flash of light against the canvas of the night sky awakens me to realize that it's actually dark already."
    "夜空のキャンバスに突然瞬いた閃光で俺は目が覚めて、辺りがすっかり真っ暗になっていることに気づく。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1781
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_b144a184:

    # "How long did I sleep? I feel groggy and can't feel my right arm."
    "俺はどれほど眠っていたのだろう？　まだ意識が朦朧としている上に、右腕の感覚がない。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1783
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_e2ecc985:

    # "As I attempt to flex it, I realize why."
    "腕を曲げようとして、その理由に気づく。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1795
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_10f78f70:

    # "Rin is leaning heavily against my shoulder, almost falling on my lap."
    "琳が俺の肩に大きくもたれかかっている。膝に落っこちそうだ。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1797
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_e04395e1:

    # "She is fast asleep, not even fazed by the fireworks."
    "すっかり眠り込んでいる。花火にも驚かない。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1799
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_0321551d:

    # "Her mouth is slightly open and her eyes are peacefully closed. A sleeping, child-like face of the innocent."
    "彼女の口はかすかに開かれ、目は穏やかにつむられている。その寝顔は無垢な子供のようだ。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1801
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_abb1be83:

    # "I shake Rin gently with my free arm, trying to wake her up or failing that, move her so that my other arm is liberated from its pinch."
    "俺は琳を起こそうとして、あるいは起こせないまでも、琳の体にはさまれている右腕を外そうとして、空いている腕でその体をそっと揺する。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1803
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_705d4475:

    # "Rin's face twitches and her eyelids shut tighter, as if to resist against waking up."
    "琳は顔をひくっと動かし、まぶたをギュッと閉じる。起きまいとしているかのようだ。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1808
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_2d1de708:

    # "She gradually opens her eyes but keeps them half-closed, letting the light from the fireworks sneak just past her eyelashes so that her green irises mirror the bright flashes of the explosions, then looks up at me and frowns."
    "彼女は段々と目を開くが、それも半開きで止まった。花火の光がまつ毛を越えて忍び寄ってくると、琳の緑色の眼にその光が映りこむ。琳は俺を見上げて眉をひそめる。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1813
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_a43d8986:

    # rin "Just a while longer, okay?"
    rin "もう少し寝かせて……"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1815
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_a17840ab:

    # "Rin's voice is drowsy and slow, leaving her almost unintelligibly muttered words hanging lazily in the air."
    "いかにも眠そうな声で、か細くつぶやく様に、むにゃむにゃと言う。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1817
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_471719f1:

    # "It seems she is not entirely aware of the situation."
    "今の状況がよくわかっていないみたいだ。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1822
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_e2439e7b:

    # "Rin's head drops back on my shoulder as she leans against me with all her weight."
    "琳はまた俺に全体重をかけるように寄りかかると、肩に頭を落とす。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1824
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_9556c70c:

    # "She snuggles against my side, trying to make herself comfortable but making me feel very uncomfortable at the same time."
    "俺に寄り添いながら快適な姿勢を探すけど、同時に俺は快適とはほど遠い状態になる。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1826
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_8c8f5173:

    # "I become intensely, almost painfully aware of Rin's warm body and the deep, peaceful movement of her chest against my arm, her breathing soon returning to the even rhythm."
    "琳の暖かい体、腕に当たる穏やかな胸の動き、次第に落ち着きを取り戻す寝息。俺はそれを強烈に、ほとんど痛いくらいに意識する。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1828
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_f299cbdd:

    # "I can't help admiring her gift for sleeping, or the ease of mind of hers to use someone she has known for less than a week as a pillow."
    "こいつの寝る才能とか、知り合って１週間も経っていない人間を枕にできる気楽さとか、尊敬せずにはいられないな。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1830
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_0605ab99:

    # "The rockets rise up to the sky one at a time, breaking into flowers of red, green and gold, accompanied by the oohs and aahs of the audience."
    "打ち上げ花火が１つずつ夜空に舞い上がり、赤や緑、金の花を描き出すと、観衆からワッと歓声が上がる。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1832
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_5261bc98:

    # "I try to push Rin's disconcerting proximity out of my mind, for what can I do about it? I just hope her short while really is that."
    "琳との距離が近すぎて落ち着かないけど、それを意識しないよう努力する。他にどうしようもないじゃないか。もう少し、というのが言葉通りであることを願うばかりだ。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1834
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_309fb3e3:

    # "One by one, the glittery bursts are born and die in a blink of an eye, coloring the dark night sky into a constantly changing abstract painting."
    "次から次へと、夜空に眩い光が一瞬生まれては消え、変幻自在の抽象画を描き出す。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1836
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_4c400eda:

    # "I listen to the low booms of the explosions and Rin's quiet breathing, trying to clear my own head of the post-awakening disorientation."
    "俺は花火の轟音と琳の静かな寝息に耳を傾けながら、目覚めたばかりでぼんやりする頭をしゃっきりさせようとする。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1838
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_eb3e1bd1:

    # "Thankfully, just a while longer really proves to be just a while, as Rin stirs from her slumber and wakes up again before the fireworks are over."
    "ありがたいことに、琳の言った『もう少し』は本当に少しだけで、花火が終わる前に琳は眠りから目覚める。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1843
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_4ec78d4e:

    # rin "I fell asleep."
    rin "寝てた"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1854
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_3bf678fe:

    # "She finally opens her eyes completely and blinks a few times."
    "とうとう琳はパッチリと眼を開け、何度かまばたきをする。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1856
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_e4a0d11d:

    # hi "You fell asleep on top of me. Twice."
    hi "お前、俺の上で寝てたんだぞ。２回も"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1861
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_2ff2ae43:

    # rin "You didn't like it?"
    rin "イヤだった？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1863
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_b259ba56:

    # hi "Err…, well…"
    hi "あ……いや……"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1868
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_1c7f2a95:

    # "Despite the inconclusive stammering, Rin sits upright, drawing herself away from me."
    "どもって要領を得なかったにも関わらず、琳はまっすぐに座り、俺から距離を置く。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1870
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_8ab47ccd:

    # hi "Well, you are heavy."
    hi "お前、重いぞ"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1872
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_365f08d6:

    # "It's a lie, she weighs next to nothing, but I have to get a jab back at her, even if it's under the belt. My mock protest fails to draw any reaction as Rin's attention is drawn upwards, to the flashes of the fireworks."
    "もちろん嘘だ。琳には重さなんてないも同然だ。でも俺は嘘でも琳に嫌味を言ってやらなきゃ気が済まなかった。俺の怒るふりに琳はまるで反応しない。琳の関心は空の、花火の閃光に惹きつけられている。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1877
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_bc7373cd:

    # "She seems hypnotized by the colorful play of the explosions."
    "色とりどりの爆発に琳はすっかり魅了されたようだ。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1879
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_60f95b98:

    # "A slight tingling sensation goes up and down in my arm as blood starts to circulate again. It's unpleasant but it helps me to get rid of this dizzy feeling."
    "また腕に血がめぐり始め、痺れるような感覚が腕を上下する。うっとうしいけど、めまいから立ち直るには丁度いい。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1881
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_1b3509ae:

    # "More and more rockets rise up to the sky, the bright colors of their explosions reflecting from the clouds."
    "さらに打ち上げ花火が舞い上がり、明るい光が雲に反射する。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1883
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_4460ad2d:

    # "Both of us stare at the fireworks fixedly through the canopy of the trees, enthralled by the show."
    "俺たちは花火の光景に心を奪われ、並木の枝葉越しにそれをじっと見つめる。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1885
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_b921a783:

    # "We would get a vastly better view of the sky if we moved even a couple of yards, but neither of us bothers to even suggest it."
    "もう２、３メートルほど位置をずらせば、もっとよく見えるだろう。けど俺も琳も、そんなことを言い出すことさえしない。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1890
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_578ac106:

    # rin "I really do like fireworks, even though looking at them makes me feel kinda sad, I think. It's like they want you to look at them so bad so they are loud and bright, but when someone looks, they are already gone."
    rin "私、花火好きなんだ。見てて悲しくなることもあるけどね。きっと花火って自分を見てもらいたいんだよ。だからあんなに音が大きくて明るいんだ でも誰かが見てくれるころには、もう消えちゃう"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1895
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_7fa00dde:

    # rin "It's like they were not even real."
    rin "まるでみんな現実じゃなかったみたいに"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1897
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_ce617998_4:

    # "…"
    "……"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1899
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_5129d926:

    # hi "They are real, I can tell you that."
    hi "いや、現実だよ。まちがいなく"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1901
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_43439291:

    # hi "All of this is… real, you know?"
    hi "これはみんな……現実なんだ。わかるだろ？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1903
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_acdee237:

    # hi "If you think about it, nothing really lasts for long. Even something like my life or yours is just a blink of an eye in the history of everything, like one of those rockets. Poof, and we're gone."
    hi "考えてみれば、どんなものだって長くは続かない。俺やお前の命だって、長い歴史の中じゃほんの一瞬でしかない。花火と同じで。『パーン！』それでおしまいさ"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1905
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_f58ffe2f:

    # hi "But we're here, aren't we?"
    hi "でも、俺たちはここにいる。そうだろ？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1907
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_953eaff5:

    # "Yeah, this is reality. Rin, sitting next to me, the loud bangs of the fireworks, the vast, unlimited sky. These things are definitely real, even though they won't stay here forever."
    "そうだ、これが現実だ。俺の隣に座る琳、花火の轟音、広く限りない空。みんな確かに存在している。たとえ、いずれは消えてしまうとしても。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1909
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_2f6b54f3:

    # "I feel warm inside, and I wonder if it's because Rin is so close to me or just the feeling of being alive."
    "自分の中に温かいものを感じる。琳がこんなにも近くにいるからなのか、それともこれが生きている実感というものなのだろうか。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1914
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_be17fdb5:

    # rin "I don't really know what I should say next."
    rin "なんて言えばいいかわからない"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1916
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_89270cad:

    # hi "It's all right… maybe I'm just talking to myself."
    hi "いいって。ただの独り言だ"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1918
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_ea2e523d:

    # hi "But you know, fireworks are pretty… but in the end isn't it somehow silly to spend so much money on a fraction of a second worth of pretty sparkles?"
    hi "でもあれだよな、花火ってのは綺麗だけどさ……結局ほんの一瞬の煌きのために、こんなに金をかけるのもバカげた話だよな？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1923
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_e3726457:

    # "Rin rips her gaze off the still ongoing spectacle and leans backwards, looking at me with a repulsed face."
    "琳はまだ打ち上がり続ける花火から勢いよく視線をそらすと、体をのけぞらせて不快そうな目で俺を見る。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1925
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_13d9f5ed:

    # rin "Wow, I never expected you to be such a cynic."
    rin "うわ、君がそんな皮肉屋だったとは思わなかった"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1927
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_367ef7d3:

    # hi "Cynic is a pretty harsh word. Rather than that, I think of myself as a realist."
    hi "皮肉屋とは手厳しいな。俺はどっちかって言えば現実主義者だぞ"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1932
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_17a6791a:

    # rin "Isn't a realist just the word for what a cynic calls himself?"
    rin "現実主義って、皮肉屋が自分のことを指して言う言葉じゃないの？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1938
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_e8a0e2cb:

    # "The final rocket goes out with a bang of silver and blue, leaving the grounds eerily silent for a moment until the crowd starts moving towards the main gate like a cattle herd."
    "最後の花火が銀や青の光を放ちながら打ち上がると、敷地内は一瞬、奇妙な沈黙に包まれる。そしてまもなく、人々は牛の群れのように正門に向かって移動し始める。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1940
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_e609f523:

    # "Wisps of gray smoke drift towards the dorms from the sports field. The pungent, sulfurous smell of gunpowder it carries along feels like it sticks to my hair and clothes."
    "灰色の煙の塊が運動場から寮に向かって昇っている。鼻をつく火薬の臭いが服や髪についてしまう気がする。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1942
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_7caf6a8d:

    # hi "Was that it?"
    hi "あれで終わりか？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1947
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_a3f20c4c:

    # rin "I think so."
    rin "たぶん"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1952
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_52d0e757:

    # "I stand up and stretch my sore back. Sleeping against a brick wall wasn't such a good idea after all."
    "俺は立ち上がって、背筋を伸ばす。レンガの壁に寄りかかって寝たのはやはり失敗だった。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1963
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_19b7bc52:

    # "Rin stands up as well and turns to face me, with an expectant gaze on her tired features."
    "琳も立ち上がって俺に向き直る。その疲れた表情に期待混じりの視線が見える。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1965
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_b1f54332:

    # "Although she seems to have trouble focusing her eyes, she is looking straight at me, something I feel has not occurred too often in the past week."
    "うまく焦点を合わせられなくなっているようだけど、琳は俺をまっすぐ見る。この一週間、琳はそれほど俺をまっすぐ見たりはしなかった気がする。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1967
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_b11f0750:

    # hi "Umm…so…"
    hi "えっと……それで……"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1969
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_4699b85c:

    # "I suddenly realize we have been almost on a date here, as if by accident. Even if we did nothing."
    "俺は突然、まるで偶然のように、今日一日ずっと琳とデート同然に過ごしていたことに気づく。何もしてなかったけど。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1971
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_c9a2c4fe:

    # "But it wasn't… so why blood is rushing to my cheeks and my speech stammering?"
    "でも、デートなんかじゃない……ならどうして頬が熱くなって、言葉に詰まるんだ？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1973
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_99424197:

    # "I don't know what I should say, especially since it seems Rin is waiting for me to say something, but luckily she solves my problem for me."
    "琳は俺の言葉を待ち続けているけど、俺はかえって何を言ったらいいかわからない。でも幸運なことに、琳の方から状況を解決してくれる。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1978
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_44ba7bce:

    # rin "Good night, Hisao."
    rin "おやすみ、久夫"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1983
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_f2a83f0c:

    # "She gives me one more lingering look, measuring me from tip to toe, turns around on her heel and skips off, disappearing into the crowd."
    "琳は俺の頭からつま先までを、見定めるようにもう一度長々と見つめる。そして振り向いて、人ごみの中に消えていく。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1987
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_ce617998_5:

    # "…"
    "……"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1989
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_2e6e077b:

    # hi "Okay… Good night."
    hi "ああ……おやすみ"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1991
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_7f8a200f:

    # "I'm left standing there, giving my response to the cooling night air."
    "俺はそこに突っ立って、冷えた夜の空気に答える。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1993
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_0bcb7f89:

    # "Sigh."
    "はあ。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1995
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_ecb49e2f:

    # "The festival turned out to be nothing like I expected."
    "結局、学園祭は俺の予想とは大分かけ離れたものとなった。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1997
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_72ba202f:

    # "I ended up spending all day in one spot with Rin, even though neither of us agreed on nor suggested that we do anything."
    "琳と一緒に、ずっと同じ場所で一日を過ごしてしまった。お互いに示しあったわけでも、何をしようと提案したわけでもないのに。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:1999
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_9f6cf52d:

    # "I just didn't have anything better to do and evidently, neither did she."
    "俺も琳も他にするべきこともなかったのだろう。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2001
translate jp a1_sunday_clouds_in_my_head_f8776d05:

    # "Rin's warmth lingers for a while longer in my body before disappearing into the falling night."
    "琳の温かみがしばらく俺の体に残っていたけど、それも夜の中に消えていく。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2016
translate jp a1_sunday_promise_of_time_36dce37f:

    # "…Right. I know what I'll do. Even if it's just one person, I'll make the festival more enjoyable for her."
    "……そうだ。俺のすべきことがわかった。たった一人だとしても、その一人が学園祭を楽しめるようにしてみせる。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2018
translate jp a1_sunday_promise_of_time_914b53c1:

    # "As I place the bowl on the counter, I call out to Lilly."
    "おわんをカウンターに置きながら、リリーに声をかける。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2023
translate jp a1_sunday_promise_of_time_6805ef3f:

    # li "Ah, Hisao. You brought it back?"
    li "あら、久夫さん。返しに来てくれたんですね？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2025
translate jp a1_sunday_promise_of_time_5c429f6f:

    # hi "Yeah, here."
    hi "ああ、これ"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2030
translate jp a1_sunday_promise_of_time_ba4b8892:

    # "I slide it into her hands, and she takes it over to someone who is apparently on cleaning duty. Considering that I didn't see them here before, it's probably a penalty for their tardiness."
    "おわんを手渡すと、リリーは皿洗いらしい人の所へそれを持っていく。さっきここで見なかった人たちだし、遅刻したことへのペナルティなんだろう。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2032
translate jp a1_sunday_promise_of_time_d407bcd4:

    # hi "Hey, Lilly?"
    hi "なあ、リリー？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2037
translate jp a1_sunday_promise_of_time_8869fe3b:

    # "She perks up and returns to the counter as she hears my voice again, realizing that I'm still here."
    "リリーは声を聞きつけ、ピンと頭を上げる。俺がまだいると気づいて、カウンターに戻ってくる。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2039
translate jp a1_sunday_promise_of_time_7c16cb29:

    # hi "Want to go see some more of the festival?"
    hi "もっと学園祭を見たくない？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2046
translate jp a1_sunday_promise_of_time_d2443f2d:

    # "She puffs her cheeks disapprovingly. It looks kind of cute, and in complete contradiction to her usually reserved nature."
    "それはできない、とほおを膨らませる彼女。ちょっとかわいい。いつもの控えめな感じとはまったく逆の仕草だ。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2048
translate jp a1_sunday_promise_of_time_fe2b9a31:

    # "It takes a few seconds for me to get what she's taking issue with. Whoops."
    "リリーが何に腹を立てているのか、気づくまでしばらくかかる。マズイ。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2050
translate jp a1_sunday_promise_of_time_1b63976a:

    # hi "Ah… um, I didn't mean to…"
    hi "あー……あの、ごめん……"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2055
translate jp a1_sunday_promise_of_time_801a4a7d:

    # "Lilly giggles at me, exposing her teasing for what it is."
    "俺を見てクスクス笑うリリーの、いたずら心が垣間見える。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2057
translate jp a1_sunday_promise_of_time_cebbf8c0:

    # li "You're still not used to the school, are you?"
    li "まだこの学校に慣れていないみたいですね？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2059
translate jp a1_sunday_promise_of_time_61abcbb1:

    # "She got me."
    "やられた。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2064
translate jp a1_sunday_promise_of_time_7c1c92a9:

    # li "Still… I kind of need to stay with our stall. It's taken until just now to even get everything unpacked."
    li "まだ……私は屋台に残らないといけないんです。荷解きを終えるのに今までかかってしまったもので"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2066
translate jp a1_sunday_promise_of_time_652fa2d9:

    # "I guess her reluctance shouldn't overly surprise me, considering how much work she's put into this."
    "この学園祭のためにどれだけがんばってきたかを考えれば、リリーがためらっているのは特に驚くことじゃない。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2068
translate jp a1_sunday_promise_of_time_8c627de8:

    # hi "Everything seems to be running fine now, though. Besides, you've got extra help on hand, anyway."
    hi "そうは言っても、だいぶうまくいき始めてるみたいだけどね。それに、手伝いの人も来てくれてるし"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2073
translate jp a1_sunday_promise_of_time_249c755c:

    # "A boy in the middle of cooking some soba noodles turns towards us, grinning."
    "そばを調理中の少年が、ニヤニヤしながら俺たちの方を振り向く。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2075
translate jp a1_sunday_promise_of_time_caa8df6c:

    # "Student" "Go on Lils, you've earned yourself a break. We can hold down the fort, for now."
    "生徒" "リリー、いいから休憩してきなよ。今は俺たちだけでどうにかするからさ"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2080
translate jp a1_sunday_promise_of_time_17119648:

    # li "If you say it's okay, then I suppose so…"
    li "そう言うのなら、まあ……"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2085
translate jp a1_sunday_promise_of_time_f3309163:

    # li "But, if you need any help—"
    li "でも、もし助けがいるときは――"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2087
translate jp a1_sunday_promise_of_time_f5d28998:

    # "Student" "Then we'll call you. Go on, we'll be fine."
    "生徒" "こっちから君を呼ぶよ。ほらほら、俺たちは大丈夫だから"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2092
translate jp a1_sunday_promise_of_time_0094ee1e:

    # "Lilly finally gives up her resistance as he waves a spatula at her. She feels her way around the back of the stall, and picks up her cane on the way."
    "彼が『行け』というようにヘラを振ると、とうとうリリーも抵抗をあきらめる。手探りで屋台の裏まで行って、そこにある自分の白杖を手に取る。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2094
translate jp a1_sunday_promise_of_time_a5e8b1a6:

    # "I guess the first thing we should do is look for Hanako. Lilly seems kind of worried about her, and I doubt she'd be the kind of person to enjoy milling about in crowds like this, all alone."
    "まずは華子を探さないといけないだろうな。リリーが心配しているようだし、華子はこんな人ごみの中を一人でぶらついて楽しむタイプじゃないだろう。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2096
translate jp a1_sunday_promise_of_time_82a913f0:

    # hi "So, I guess we should search for Hanako. Where to, first?"
    hi "じゃあ、華子を探すってことになるかな。まずどこに行こうか？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2101
translate jp a1_sunday_promise_of_time_0dd3a347:

    # li "Hmm…"
    li "うーん……"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2103
translate jp a1_sunday_promise_of_time_9401b0ca:

    # "The both of us go quiet for a moment to think."
    "二人して黙りこみ、少し考える。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2105
translate jp a1_sunday_promise_of_time_add108a6:

    # hi "Maybe she's in her dorm room?"
    hi "寮の部屋にいるんじゃないかな？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2107
translate jp a1_sunday_promise_of_time_4e52f808:

    # li "I doubt it. She doesn't keep too many things in there, so she'd have nothing to do."
    li "どうでしょう。華ちゃんは部屋にあまり物を置いていないので、することがないでしょうし"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2112
translate jp a1_sunday_promise_of_time_d3ec3453:

    # li "…Ah! The library?"
    li "……あ！　図書室は？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2114
translate jp a1_sunday_promise_of_time_bafc55a9:

    # "As good a place as any to search for an avid reader, I suppose."
    "本の虫を探すにはいい場所かもしれない。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2116
translate jp a1_sunday_promise_of_time_b363c4e7:

    # hi "The library it is. We'll check there first, then."
    hi "図書室だな。じゃあ、最初に調べてみよう"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2123
translate jp a1_sunday_promise_of_time_e5167dba:

    # "Aside from the muffled sounds of the crowd seeping in from outside, the inside of the school seems almost deserted."
    "漏れ聞こえるくぐもった雑踏の音を除けば、校舎内はかなりひっそりしている。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2125
translate jp a1_sunday_promise_of_time_72a8bec8:

    # "In order to make sure everyone had enough room, I guess all the events were organized to be held outside, on school grounds. They're definitely quite large, by any other school's standards."
    "全員に十分なスペースを与えるために、催しは全て外のグラウンドで行うようになっているんだろう。他の学校に比べ、ここの学園祭は明らかに大規模だ。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2130
translate jp a1_sunday_promise_of_time_bdcdfede:

    # li "It's nice and quiet in here, isn't it?"
    li "ここは静かで良いですね"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2132
translate jp a1_sunday_promise_of_time_9f7790c5:

    # hi "Yeah. Much nicer than the hustle and bustle outside."
    hi "ああ。外の騒がしさよりよっぽどいいよ"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2139
translate jp a1_sunday_promise_of_time_ae12b331:

    # "We take our time and slowly walk through the first floor of the school, eventually reaching the stairs to the second floor."
    "俺たちはゆっくり校舎の１階を通り、２階へ続く階段にたどり着く。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2145
translate jp a1_sunday_promise_of_time_12c8816c:

    # "I can't help but notice how Lilly anticipates every door and obstacle, her cane remaining still and her hand skating along the hallway railings."
    "いかにリリーがドアや障害物を見越しているか気づく。白杖は持ったまま、廊下の手すりに沿って手を滑らせている。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2147
translate jp a1_sunday_promise_of_time_6f972e78:

    # hi "You really know the school well, don't you?"
    hi "学園のことをよくわかってるんだね"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2152
translate jp a1_sunday_promise_of_time_394e2997:

    # "She smiles and nods straight ahead."
    "リリーは笑ってこくりとうなずく。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2154
translate jp a1_sunday_promise_of_time_cfde3ad2:

    # li "I've been here for a few years now, so I know where everything is."
    li "私は何年もここにいますから、何がどこにあるかくらいはわかります"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2159
translate jp a1_sunday_promise_of_time_df8c6a32:

    # li "The dorms still trip me up though, sometimes. I haven't been there as long, and they're not as well laid-out as the main building."
    li "まだ時々寮で迷うことはあるんですけどね。ここほど長く過ごしていませんし、本館ほど作りがよくないので"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2161
translate jp a1_sunday_promise_of_time_d6cb0e5e:

    # li "If I'm remembering right, they used to be unused buildings before being renovated and used as dormitories."
    li "私の記憶が確かなら、改築して寮として使われる前は使用されていない建物だったはずです"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2163
translate jp a1_sunday_promise_of_time_5a6aee01:

    # "That explains why the male and female dorms looked different from the outside, and why their rooms seem kind of unusual for sleeping quarters."
    "それで男子寮と女子寮の見た目が違う理由がわかった。女子寮の部屋が、寝泊まりする部屋にしては変わって見える理由も。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2165
translate jp a1_sunday_promise_of_time_f07995f0:

    # "I'd assumed she'd been living in the dormitories since she began attending the school, but now I'm reminded of what she said yesterday."
    "リリーは学園に通い始めたときから寮で暮らしていたんだろうと思っていた。けど、昨日彼女が言ったことを思い出す。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2167
translate jp a1_sunday_promise_of_time_bfc6474c:

    # hi "That's right, you mentioned that before."
    hi "そうだ、前に言ってたね"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2169
translate jp a1_sunday_promise_of_time_9ab42921:

    # hi "I'd assumed that most of the students here lived in the dormitories once they enrolled. A lot of them seem to, in any case."
    hi "入学したら、ほとんどの生徒は寮に住むのかと思ってたよ。少なくとも、大体の人はそうしてるみたいだし"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2174
translate jp a1_sunday_promise_of_time_89cb5046:

    # "Lilly's expression becomes somewhat harder to read, my questioning evidently touching on a delicate point."
    "リリーの表情が少し読みづらくなる。俺の質問は、明らかにデリケートな点に触れたようだ。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2176
translate jp a1_sunday_promise_of_time_1fbb1998:

    # li "Well… How should I say…"
    li "そうですね……どう言えばいいか……"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2181
translate jp a1_sunday_promise_of_time_ed3efaf2:

    # li "Everyone… has their reasons."
    li "みんな……それぞれの理由があるんですよ"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2183
translate jp a1_sunday_promise_of_time_7258c539:

    # "Something tells me that one of those with 'reasons' is Hanako, hence her tiptoeing around the answer. My own predicament is yet another such case."
    "きっと、華子は『理由』のある生徒の一人なのだろう。だからこそ、リリーは直接的な答えを避ける。俺自身の状況もまた、同じようなものだ。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2185
translate jp a1_sunday_promise_of_time_b3c6b3dd:

    # "I guess it's a choice everyone here would have to make for themselves… or, in my instance, have made for them."
    "ここに住むかどうかは、誰もが自分で決めなくてはならないんだろう……俺の場合は、決められてしまった。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2187
translate jp a1_sunday_promise_of_time_2f111832:

    # hi "It can't be helped, I suppose. At least Yamaku itself seems like a nice place."
    hi "それはまあ、仕方ないんだろうな。それでも、山久自体はいい所みたいだけど"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2192
translate jp a1_sunday_promise_of_time_40b615e8:

    # li "It's good to hear you say that. I'd thought you were coming to dislike it."
    li "そう言ってくれて良かったです。てっきり嫌いになっているかと"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2194
translate jp a1_sunday_promise_of_time_9898b371:

    # hi "What about you, though?"
    hi "でも、君はどうなの？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2199
translate jp a1_sunday_promise_of_time_5daa70a3:

    # "My reversal of Lilly's statement takes her by surprise."
    "この切り返しに、リリーは驚く。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2201
translate jp a1_sunday_promise_of_time_d6c70ea1:

    # li "I've been here for a while, so…"
    li "ずっとここにいましたし、なので……"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2203
translate jp a1_sunday_promise_of_time_d5b25289:

    # hi "It's not that. You just seemed pretty depressed about Akira."
    hi "そうじゃなくてさ。ただ、晃さんのことで落ち込んでるみたいだったから"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2208
translate jp a1_sunday_promise_of_time_786da88c:

    # li "Hmm~"
    li "う～ん"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2210
translate jp a1_sunday_promise_of_time_5681d9a5:

    # hi "What's with that look?"
    hi "その顔はなんなのさ？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2215
translate jp a1_sunday_promise_of_time_49dd2c8e:

    # li "Akira's taken. Sorry, Hisao."
    li "姉さんは予約済みですよ。残念でしたね、久夫さん"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2217
translate jp a1_sunday_promise_of_time_50b500cd:

    # "Lilly never sees how fast my palm meets my face at her sly accusation."
    "このからかいに呆れたジェスチャーを取った俺を、リリーは見ることもできない。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2219
translate jp a1_sunday_promise_of_time_f3de2019:

    # hi "Hey, I was worried about you. That's no way to respond to concern."
    hi "なあ、心配してたんだぜ。そんな言い方ってないだろう"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2224
translate jp a1_sunday_promise_of_time_57d85c1e:

    # "While she gives an amused grin, we round the corner of the hallway and enter the library."
    "リリーのからかうような微笑みと共に、俺たちは廊下の角を曲がって図書室に入る。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2229
translate jp a1_sunday_promise_of_time_4348f201:

    # "As we do so, it isn't hard to spot Hanako, considering that the room is completely devoid of anyone else."
    "入ってしまうと、華子は簡単に見つかる。他に誰も部屋にいないからだ。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2234
translate jp a1_sunday_promise_of_time_dcae37e8:

    # "Given that there are no staff around, I guess there's no need to heed the usual library rules. I call out to her."
    "周りに職員はいないし、いつもの図書室の規則に気を使う必要はないだろう。俺は華子に呼びかける。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2236
translate jp a1_sunday_promise_of_time_5990f38d:

    # hi "Hey, Hanako."
    hi "おーい、華子"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2241
translate jp a1_sunday_promise_of_time_bc1e785c:

    # li "Hanako is here?"
    li "華ちゃん、いるんですか？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2243
translate jp a1_sunday_promise_of_time_b5f0c77b:

    # "As she hears our voices, Hanako's head flicks up from behind a book, probably the same one she'd been reading on Friday."
    "俺たちの声を聞くと、華子の頭が本の陰からひょっこり現れる。たぶん、金曜日に読んでいた本と同じものだ。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2253
translate jp a1_sunday_promise_of_time_382d8b41:

    # ha "Hisao… Lilly?"
    ha "中井君に……リリー？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2255
translate jp a1_sunday_promise_of_time_44aa898d:

    # hi "Just thought we'd drop by. Lilly just managed to escape from the noodle stall, with a little help."
    hi "少し寄ってみようかと思ってね。ちょっとした手助けもあって、リリーは屋台から逃げてきたところなんだ"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2260
translate jp a1_sunday_promise_of_time_85d30a08:

    # li "That wasn't really an escape…"
    li "逃げてきたわけでは……"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2266
translate jp a1_sunday_promise_of_time_3b6e73ca:

    # "Hanako gives a small giggle, briefly surprising both of us."
    "俺たち二人に少し面食らって、華子はクスクスと笑う。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2271
translate jp a1_sunday_promise_of_time_93a2fe78:

    # ha "I just thought that… Lilly might not be enjoying the festival."
    ha "私、ちょうど考えてたんです……リリーは学園祭を楽しんでないんじゃないかって"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2273
translate jp a1_sunday_promise_of_time_69f89abf:

    # hi "Well, now we can enjoy it together, right?"
    hi "まあ、これで一緒に楽しめるだろ？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2278
translate jp a1_sunday_promise_of_time_a9547d75:

    # "The two nod happily before we set out of the library and towards the festivities."
    "二人は楽しそうにうなずき、俺たちは図書室から学園祭へと向かう。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2289
translate jp a1_sunday_promise_of_time_ae7cf5b0:

    # "I hand over some change to the girl behind the counter, and take the two styrofoam cups of tea. I try to accentuate my bow a bit to cover for the fact that she's quite obviously deaf."
    "売り子の少女にいくらか小銭を渡して、紅茶の入った二つのスチロールコップを受け取る。その子は明らかに聴覚障害だ。気持ち大げさに会釈をする。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2291
translate jp a1_sunday_promise_of_time_89978960:

    # "Come to think of it, I probably should have asked for help instead of leaving those two in the gardens while I bought drinks."
    "二人を校庭に待たせるんじゃなくて、手伝いを頼むべきだったかもしれない。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2293
translate jp a1_sunday_promise_of_time_3236443b:

    # "Trying to juggle the two cups of hot tea (for them) and a can of coffee (for myself, out of a vending machine) isn't exactly easy."
    "熱い紅茶のコップを二つ（二人の分）落とさないようにしながら、缶コーヒー（自分用、自動販売機で買った）を持つのは簡単じゃない。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2295
translate jp a1_sunday_promise_of_time_11d06e2e:

    # "With some careful maneuvering, though, I manage to keep everything stable and upright as I walk over to the bench where Lilly and Hanako are sitting and chatting."
    "とはいえ、巧みな技によって何とかバランスを保ちつつ、リリーと華子が座っておしゃべりをしているベンチまで歩いて行く。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2302
translate jp a1_sunday_promise_of_time_dd59d3e6:

    # "It's actually quite a nice place. Lit only by moonlight, it's tucked away some distance from the main events."
    "本当にいい場所だ。月明かりだけに照らされ、本会場から少し離れた隠れスポット。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2304
translate jp a1_sunday_promise_of_time_f115cd7c:

    # "Compared to how hot it had been during the day, this spot is also pleasantly cool by now."
    "日中のひどい暑さと比べると、今のこの場所は十分に涼しい。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2306
translate jp a1_sunday_promise_of_time_5e03238e:

    # "Not that it matters all that much. Most of the visitors have moved to areas that are either closer to the fireworks, or higher on the hill in order to view the display apparently planned."
    "それが大事だってわけでもない。予定されていたらしい打ち上げ花火を見るために、ほとんどの来場者はより花火に近い場所か、見晴らしのいい丘の高台に移動していた。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2311
translate jp a1_sunday_promise_of_time_089b6139:

    # li "Welcome back, Hisao."
    li "お帰りなさい、久夫さん"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2316
translate jp a1_sunday_promise_of_time_a2327c8a:

    # "Her ears are good. I'm not exactly close and even Hanako hadn't noticed me."
    "リリーは耳がいい。俺はそれほど近づいていたわけではないし、華子さえ俺に気づいていなかった。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2318
translate jp a1_sunday_promise_of_time_bb7e83a0:

    # hi "Here you go. Sorry it's instant, but that's all they had left by now."
    hi "お待ちどうさま。ごめんインスタントで。もうこれしか残ってなかったんだ"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2320
translate jp a1_sunday_promise_of_time_824d179c:

    # "Hanako gingerly takes a cup from my right hand, and I gently place the other into Lilly's outstretched hands."
    "華子は俺の右手からコップを恐る恐る受け取る。差し出されたリリーの手に、俺はそっともう片方を手渡す。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2326
translate jp a1_sunday_promise_of_time_cdca091b:

    # li "Did you enjoy the festival then, Hisao?"
    li "学園祭は楽しめたみたいですね、久夫さん？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2328
translate jp a1_sunday_promise_of_time_724736c9:

    # hi "Yeah, it was pretty fun."
    hi "ああ、すごく面白かったよ"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2330
translate jp a1_sunday_promise_of_time_397b3a35:

    # "An honest answer. Much of the food may have been somewhat subpar, but it was a lot of fun in the end, especially with Hanako and Lilly."
    "素直な感想だ。まあ、食べ物はほとんど今ひとつだったかもしれないけど、それでもかなり楽しかった。華子とリリーと一緒だから。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2332
translate jp a1_sunday_promise_of_time_d00d3fcb:

    # "In fact, I think those two may have enjoyed themselves even more than I did. With both Lilly and me around, much of Hanako's withdrawn nature around others died down enough for her to enjoy herself."
    "実際は、この二人の方が俺より楽しんでいたのかもしれない。リリーと俺のそばだと、他人へ見せる華子の内気な性格は、学園祭を楽しめるぐらいまでに落ち着いていた。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2345
translate jp a1_sunday_promise_of_time_e5fb45a6:

    # "As we sit drinking, the whistle of the first firework rings out before it explodes into a vibrant shower of blue against the night sky, heralding the beginning of the end for the festival."
    "俺たちが座って飲んでいると、花火の上がる笛のような音が聞こえる。夜空に派手な青いシャワーが降りそそぎ、学園祭が終わりに近いことを告げる。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2347
translate jp a1_sunday_promise_of_time_3567575a:

    # "Enthusiastic shouts can be heard from the crowds scattered around the school grounds celebrating them."
    "学園のグラウンドに散らばった人ごみから、それをもてはやす興奮した歓声が聞こえる。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2349
translate jp a1_sunday_promise_of_time_17f24370:

    # "For minutes on end, Hanako and I watch the fireworks overhead as Lilly blissfully listens to them with her eyes shut."
    "しばらくの間、華子と俺は頭上に上がる花火を眺め、リリーは目を閉じて幸せそうに音を聞く。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2351
translate jp a1_sunday_promise_of_time_53abc8d7:

    # "Red, green, yellow, star-shaped, circular and patterned, and all manner of shapes and colors fill the air, one after the other, and dance across the sky."
    "赤、緑、黄色、星形、円形模様、あらゆる形や色が、次から次へと辺りを満たし、空を舞う。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2353
translate jp a1_sunday_promise_of_time_b17d8706:

    # "No place near where I lived put on such lavish displays. Festivals like this were a thing of the past in such a metropolitan area."
    "俺が暮らしていた近所のどんな場所にもこんな贅沢な見せ物はなかった。こういった学園祭は都市圏では過去のものだ。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2355
translate jp a1_sunday_promise_of_time_c95895da:

    # "To be seeing such a sight with these two… it's probably the happiest I've been in a long while."
    "こんな光景を、この二人と見る……ここしばらくで一番幸せなことじゃないだろうか。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2363
translate jp a1_sunday_promise_of_time_8327ed47:

    # li "So… that's it. The festival's finally ending."
    li "と……いうことで。とうとう学園祭も終わりですね"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2365
translate jp a1_sunday_promise_of_time_142d50b9:

    # hi "Yeah."
    hi "そうだな"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2367
translate jp a1_sunday_promise_of_time_e624e405:

    # "She gives a delicate, wistful sigh."
    "リリーは繊細で、切ないため息をつく。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2372
translate jp a1_sunday_promise_of_time_9c529ad3:

    # li "As much as I might complain about all the stuff we have to do, it's still sad that we'll have graduated before the next Yamaku festival."
    li "きっとまた仕事の多さに不平を言うことになるでしょうけど、やっぱり私たちが次の学園祭の前に卒業してしまうのは残念ですね"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2377
translate jp a1_sunday_promise_of_time_b85cb94a:

    # "I walk forwards and stand beside Lilly, gently resting a hand on her shoulder."
    "俺はリリーのそばに行き、そっと肩に手を置く。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2379
translate jp a1_sunday_promise_of_time_1ccc94fb:

    # hi "Don't worry. We still have Tanabata later in the year, right?"
    hi "気にするなよ。まだ今年の七夕があるじゃないか"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2384
translate jp a1_sunday_promise_of_time_e20d9f96:

    # li "You're right. It would be nice to go there when it comes."
    li "そうですね。その時には、行けるといいですね"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2386
translate jp a1_sunday_promise_of_time_9b8ff013:

    # "Minutes of silence pass, with only the blasts of the fireworks to be heard."
    "しばし沈黙が続く。聴こえてくるのは花火の散る音だけだ。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2388
translate jp a1_sunday_promise_of_time_ffcbc052:

    # "Seeing these two reminds me of those words of advice Lilly had given me as we walked into town together."
    "この二人を見ていると、一緒に町を歩きながらリリーがアドバイスしてくれた言葉を思い出す。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2390
translate jp a1_sunday_promise_of_time_df57efe4:

    # "'Cherish the opportunity to make new friends', huh?"
    "『新しい友達を作るというのは素晴らしいことですよ』、か。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2392
translate jp a1_sunday_promise_of_time_d407bcd4_1:

    # hi "Hey, Lilly?"
    hi "なあ、リリー？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2397
translate jp a1_sunday_promise_of_time_ca163cba:

    # "She turns her head slightly to show that she's listening, Hanako's gaze still firmly fixed on the technicolor fireworks bursting overhead."
    "リリーは聞いていることを示すために、わずかにこっちを向く。華子は頭上に広がる色鮮やかな花火にまだ目が釘付けになっている。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2399
translate jp a1_sunday_promise_of_time_c65427d9:

    # hi "You mind if I join you two for tea every now and again?"
    hi "時々さ、君たち二人と一緒にお茶を飲んでもいいかな？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2401
translate jp a1_sunday_promise_of_time_ebec10de:

    # "The smile on her face is more than enough to see her answer."
    "リリーの笑顔は、答えを知るには十分だ。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2406
translate jp a1_sunday_promise_of_time_79f71ed2:

    # li "It would be a pleasure, Hisao."
    li "ええ、もちろん。久夫さん"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2426
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_f8055ca2:

    # "Lilly doesn’t look impressed at all, and I can't really blame her."
    "リリーは全然楽しそうじゃない。でも、彼女が悪いわけじゃない。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2428
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_5e4bef56:

    # "On top of her issues with her stall, she still seems to be worried about Hanako."
    "屋台の問題に加えて、華子のこともまだ気にしているみたいだ。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2430
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_1fd530bc:

    # "I can't really help her with the former, so I guess the only way I can help is by trying to take her mind off our shy mutual friend."
    "屋台のほうは力になれそうもないから、俺たちの恥ずかしがりな友達のほうをひきうけて、リリーの気を楽にしてやることくらいしか、俺にはできないだろう。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2432
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_d52ae71e:

    # "Placing the bowl back on the counter, I call out to Lilly."
    "おわんをカウンターの上に戻しながら、リリーに声をかける。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2434
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_c701dc91:

    # hi "Hey, Lilly, don't worry about Hanako. I'll go find her and hang out with her, okay?"
    hi "なぁ、リリー、華子のことは大丈夫だよ。俺が見つけて、ついててやるからさ"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2439
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_8c823150:

    # "I can see Lilly's relief plainly written across her face."
    "安堵の気持ちが、はっきりとリリーの顔に浮かぶのがわかる。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2441
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_4d815a7e:

    # li "Thanks Hisao. And if you see anyone from my class, can you tell them to come back here please?"
    li "ありがとう、久夫さん。それと、私のクラスの生徒を見かけたら、ここに戻るよう伝えていただけますか？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2443
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_c7813ef5:

    # hi "Will do. Have a good one. And make sure you take a break, okay?"
    hi "わかったよ。じゃあな。あと、ちゃんと休憩とりなよ"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2448
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_ac45f748:

    # li "I will if I can. See you later, Hisao."
    li "できればそうします。ではまた、久夫さん"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2457
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_2fa30d88:

    # "I leave Lilly in the stall and head out in search of Hanako."
    "リリーを屋台に残して、華子を探しに出発する。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2459
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_b1cd5e19:

    # "In a way, I feel bad for leaving her with the crowds, but even though she was clearly under pressure, I can't help but think that she is enjoying herself."
    "リリーにたくさんの客を任せてこの場を離れることには、心苦しさを覚えないでもない。でも、明らかにプレッシャーのかかっている状況だけど、彼女ならきっとベストをつくすんだろうな。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2469
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_fd0ada46:

    # "The halls are packed with swaying crowds meandering throughout the festival."
    "廊下は、会場中をうろうろ歩き回る来場者たちでごったがえしている。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2471
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_56cbd4e4:

    # "If there's one thing I know about Hanako, it's that she's not going to be anywhere near this."
    "華子はここの近くにはいない。これだけは自信を持って言える。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2473
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_4c3d33c5:

    # "And with the students showing their friends and family their dorms, I doubt she'll be there either."
    "寮には、友達や家族を案内している生徒がいるから、あそこにもいないだろう。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2475
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_3dac0cf7:

    # "Following blind intuition, I move against the grain of the crowd."
    "自分でもよくわからない直感に従って、俺は人ごみに逆らって進む。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2477
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_1312ab66:

    # "Thankfully, this crowd seems to be slightly less festive than your usual festival crowd; I assume this is out of consideration for the student body."
    "ありがたいことに、この学園祭の来場者たちは、普段お祭りで見かける群衆と比べると少しおとなしいみたいだ――ここの生徒のみんなに気を使ってのことなんだろうな。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2481
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_f5b8e67c:

    # "As I force my way through the masses, it doesn't take long for them to thin down into nothingness."
    "人ごみをかき分けながら進んでいくと、すぐに人の数は減っていって、やがて誰一人いなくなる。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2486
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_44a0d06e:

    # "This is not surprising, since I am standing before the library."
    "驚くようなことじゃない。俺が立っているのは図書室の前なんだから。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2488
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_dcb4c0c7:

    # "Even the most eager of students don't bother to show anyone this section of the school."
    "どれだけ熱心な生徒でも、わざわざ学校のこんな場所にまで、誰かを案内したりはしないだろう。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2494
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_40d2c500:

    # "As I enter the library, the noise of the festival fades into a dull background noise, and soon I am in the reading area at the rear of the room."
    "図書室に入ると、学園祭の喧騒はごく小さな雑音ほどにまで小さくなり、俺はすぐに図書室の後ろの読書エリアへと足を運ぶ。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2496
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_27c80a8b:

    # "Behind one of the partitioned desks I see the top of a head, with straight, dark hair catching my eye."
    "ついたてで仕切られて並ぶ机の向こう側に、ストレートの黒髪に覆われた頭のてっぺんが目に留まる。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2498
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_f8a0ce17:

    # hi "Hey, Hanako. I had a feeling I'd find you here…"
    hi "やぁ、華子。ここで会えるんじゃないかって……"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2507
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_8bd62c36:

    # "The head jumps a little in shock before slowly peeping over the partition."
    "その頭は、びっくりして少し跳ねると、ついたての上からゆっくりあたりをうかがう。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2509
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_f3decb73:

    # ha "H-Hisao?"
    ha "ひ、久夫くん？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2511
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_5a9aa090:

    # hi "Hey. Lilly's pretty busy, so she sent me to find you."
    hi "よっ。リリーがすごく忙しいんで、代わりに様子を見て来てくれって言われてさ"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2516
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_849f327f:

    # ha "O-oh. Do you want to sit down?"
    ha "そ、そうですか。座ります？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2518
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_a742160e:

    # hi "Actually, I am feeling a little hungry. Would you like to get something to eat from one of the stands?"
    hi "実は、ちょっと腹が減ってるんだ。屋台で食べるもの買ってこないか？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2523
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_88deeb46:

    # ha "Um… I… I brought some food so…"
    ha "あの……わ……私、食事を用意してて……"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2525
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_53334aab:

    # "I shouldn't be surprised, but it was worth a try. Expecting her to go outside today was a long shot."
    "予想できた答えではあるけど、聞いてみてよかった。今日、華子を外に連れていくのは、まず無理だろうから。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2527
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_f9a22a35:

    # hi "How about we eat in the tea room? I passed by it on the way here, and no one was around."
    hi "華子たちの喫茶室で食べないか？　ここに来る途中で見たら、誰もいなかったし"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2529
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_0970a6fc:

    # hi "We can make some food there, and it'll be a little more comfortable. What do you say?"
    hi "あそこならちょっとした食事も用意できるし、もう少しくつろげるし。どう？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2534
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_7219cee3:

    # ha "S-sure. Let's go."
    ha "わ、わかりました。行きましょう"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2539
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_3046b7ac:

    # "Hanako closes her book and puts it away with deliberate, practiced movements."
    "華子は本を閉じると、慣れた手つきで丁寧にしまう。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2541
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_1a642705:

    # hi "Good to go?"
    hi "もういいか？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2546
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_0a3cf307:

    # ha "Y…yeah."
    ha "う……うん"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2553
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_7cbf9b7a:

    # "We walk side-by-side from the library to the tea room."
    "俺と華子は並んで、図書室から喫茶室まで歩く。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2555
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_bf4f3c70:

    # "As expected, there is barely a soul around."
    "予想通り、周りにはほとんど誰もいない。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2557
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_4c209252:

    # "If it weren't for the murmurs through the walls, you wouldn't tell that there was a huge festival going on outside."
    "壁越しに聞こえるざわめきさえなければ、外で大きな学園祭が行われているなんてわからないだろう。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2562
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_a158b664:

    # "Hanako carries her bag in both hands and focuses on just the floor ahead of her."
    "華子は両手でかばんを抱え、文字通り目の前の床を見つめている。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2570
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_161f1d88:

    # "Every now and again, she seems to break her pace a little and steps in slightly shorter paces."
    "ときどき、華子は歩幅を少し乱して、ちょっと短い歩幅で歩いているようだ。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2572
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_4b2b3256:

    # "The first time it happened, I gave it no mind, but I soon notice that she does it on a regular basis."
    "最初は特に気にしなかったけど、しょっちゅうそういう歩き方をしていることにすぐ気づく。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2574
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_dd0872f3:

    # hi "Are you all right?"
    hi "大丈夫か？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2579
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_9a2135ec:

    # "She stops dead in her tracks."
    "華子は急に立ち止まる。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2581
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_c4e512f1:

    # ha "W-what?"
    ha "な、なんですか？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2583
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_bbe29721:

    # hi "I dunno… it looked like you were tripping or something…"
    hi "わかんないんだけど……つまずいてるみたいっていうか……"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2590
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_0c31814b:

    # "A pink blush rises into her cheeks as her gaze returns to the floor."
    "華子の頬がピンクに染まり、目線は床へと戻る。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2595
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_86eb92b2:

    # ha "It… it's nothing."
    ha "な……なんでもないんです"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2597
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_c4526034:

    # hi "You know, when you say 'nothing' like that, people are inspired to ask further questions."
    hi "あのさ、そんなふうに『なんでもない』って言われたら、もっと聞きたくなるもんだよ"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2599
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_948e916d:

    # "For a second I don't think she is going to answer."
    "答えてくれないんじゃないかと一瞬思う。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2601
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_ca4123ab:

    # "Prepared to leave it be, I almost set off walking again, when…"
    "気にしないことにして、もう一度歩き出そうとする、ちょうどそのとき……"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2606
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_90451d62:

    # ha "It's a… a game."
    ha "遊び……なんです"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2608
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_0b902218:

    # hi "Game?"
    hi "遊び？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2613
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_91265327:

    # ha "Do you… see the floor here?"
    ha "ここの床……わかりますか？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2615
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_28346c38:

    # "What a bizarre question. The floor looks just like any other floor; covered in those tiles made up from squares of linoleum."
    "おかしな質問だな。他の床と変わったところはない――リノリウムの正方形が形づくるタイルに覆われた床だ。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2617
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_df08127b:

    # "Nothing noteworthy."
    "目立つようなものは何もない。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2619
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_128ee150:

    # hi "Well, yes. What about it?"
    hi "そりゃ、わかるけど。それがどうかした？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2624
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_fc0038c2:

    # ha "Sometimes… when there's no one around… I only step on the darker ones…"
    ha "ときどき……近くに誰もいないとき……黒っぽいタイルの上だけを踏んで……"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2626
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_9ff1ac7d:

    # "Hanako's voice trails off as her explanation continues, until I can barely hear her voice over the roaring silence of the empty hall."
    "説明が続くにつれ、華子の声は次第に小さくなっていき、誰もいない廊下の、耳が痛くなるような静寂の中でも、その声はほとんど聞こえなくなる。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2628
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_ce719d65:

    # hi "Darker ones?"
    hi "黒っぽいタイル？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2630
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_f836f5e4:

    # "Shuffling her feet, Hanako points the toe of her shoe at a tile that is barely a shade darker than the others."
    "華子はもじもじと足を動かして、他よりわずかに黒い色合いのタイルをつま先で指す。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2635
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_fef01370:

    # ha "L-like these ones."
    ha "こ、こういうの"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2637
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_a2c6161a:

    # hi "Oh, right, so these ones are no good?"
    hi "ああ、そういうことか、じゃあこれとかはダメなんだ？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2639
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_6ae3c9cd:

    # "I point out a nearby tile."
    "俺は近くのタイルを指す。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2644
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_67bcbbc8:

    # ha "Y-yeah. Something… something like that."
    ha "う、うん。そんな……そんな感じ"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2646
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_ea5c93ba:

    # hi "Oh, I see. Do you play this game a lot?"
    hi "ああ、なるほどね。この遊び、よくやるの？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2651
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_2b0471a6:

    # "Hanako shakes her head."
    "華子はかぶりを振る。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2653
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_db97bacc:

    # hi "Just when the halls are empty?"
    hi "廊下に人がいないときだけ？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2658
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_5c9ff614:

    # "She nods."
    "彼女はうなずく。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2660
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_46887487:

    # hi "Well then, no point in stopping, I'm beginning to get really hungry."
    hi "なら、立ち止まっててもしょうがないな。すごく腹減ってきたし"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2665
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_94469c93:

    # "She nods again, this time with a little more enthusiasm."
    "彼女はもう一度うなずく。今度はもう少し熱っぽく。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2667
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_b95f95ac:

    # hi "Well then, let's go."
    hi "じゃあ、行こう"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2674
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_479bb10a:

    # "We set off down the hall, and this time I notice that Hanako is paying a little less attention to the floor."
    "廊下を歩き出すと、華子が今度は床にあまり気を配っていないのに気づく。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2676
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_5b471535:

    # "I wonder; just how lonely does someone have to be to come up with a game like that?"
    "俺は思う――どれくらい孤独なら、人はこんな遊びを思い付くんだろう？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2678
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_b8fdacf5:

    # "But, before I realize what I'm doing, I find myself trying to aim each step so it lands on the correct tiles."
    "だけど気がつくと、俺自身も一足一足踏むべきタイルを踏もうとしている。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2685
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_fb7dd7d6:

    # "The noise of the festival is slightly louder inside the tea room, but the breeze coming through the open window makes it worth it."
    "喫茶室の中では、学園祭の喧噪は少し耳につくけど、開いた窓から吹き込む風がそれを埋め合わせてくれる。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2687
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_b74cabfe:

    # "Without thinking, I walk to the windowsill and inhale deeply. I sometimes forget how clean the air is here compared to back home."
    "無意識のうちに、窓辺に歩み寄って大きく深呼吸をする。ときどき俺は、ここの空気が実家と比べてどれほど綺麗かを忘れてしまう。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2692
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_fbf244c1:

    # ha "Do… would you like some tea?"
    ha "紅茶、いり……いかがですか？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2694
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_7ae15057:

    # hi "That would be great, thanks."
    hi "いただくよ、ありがとう"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2699
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_5a477179:

    # "It occurs to me that this is the first time I've been alone with Hanako without her trying to be somewhere else."
    "気づいたんだけど、華子と二人きりのときに、彼女が他のところに行きたそうなそぶりを見せないのは初めてだ。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2701
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_937acc64:

    # "Turning from the window, I watch as she makes a simple pot of tea and arranges some sandwiches onto a plate."
    "窓から向き直って、彼女が紅茶をシンプルなポットに淹れ、皿にサンドイッチを用意してくれている姿を見つめる。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2703
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_cd9010a8:

    # "I've seen her do this before a number of times, but this time she seems slightly different."
    "前にも華子がこういうことをするのを見たことはあるけど、今度は少し違っている。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2705
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_f570b28e:

    # "It's like she's…{w} calm."
    "なんというか……{w}穏やかなんだ。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2707
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_b01661c5:

    # "Eventually she places the small tray on the table and pours two cups of tea."
    "やがて華子は小さなトレイをテーブルに乗せ、カップ２つに紅茶を注いでくれる。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2709
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_5a5a9965:

    # "The fresh scent of brewed tea mingles with the breeze, and for a second I feel like I'm the only one in the world."
    "淹れたての紅茶の新鮮な香りがそよ風といりまじって、一瞬自分が世界でただ一人の人間のように感じる。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2711
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_74fad1d4:

    # hi "I think I know why you like this room now."
    hi "華子がこの部屋が好きだっていうの、わかる気がする"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2716
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_337e7c90:

    # ha "Um… I don't know what you mean."
    ha "その……どういうことですか？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2718
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_775b8457:

    # hi "Well, there are quite a few people out there, but in here it's like another world."
    hi "つまりさ、外にはたくさん人がいるのに、この中は別の世界みたいだろ"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2720
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_9defa7a7:

    # hi "You can pretend that there's no one around for miles."
    hi "ここからずっと遠くまで、人っ子一人いないみたいにふるまったっていいわけだ"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2725
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_c893bd8f:

    # ha "Y-you're right."
    ha "そ、そうですね"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2727
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_756116a2:

    # ha "It's like the world has forgotten this room."
    ha "まるで、世界がこの部屋のことを忘れてしまっているみたいです"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2732
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_8858f6da:

    # ha "And b-because of that, you can forget about the outside."
    ha "だ、だから、外のことも忘れてしまっていいんです"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2734
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_a332d12e:

    # "That would be appealing in some cases."
    "場合によっては、そういう考えが魅力的に感じられることもあるだろう。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2736
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_4b5608b8:

    # "As far as I can tell, conventional bullying doesn't exist in this school."
    "俺の知るかぎり、昔からあるようないじめは、この学校には存在しない。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2738
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_acb8dcdb:

    # "But then again, I haven't seen a single person talk to Hanako besides Lilly."
    "といっても、華子に話しかけた人を、リリーの他には一人も見たことがない。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2740
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_944bd62a:

    # "If you're ignored by the world, a place where you can forget its existence would hold a special appeal."
    "世界から無視される人にとって、世界の存在を忘れることのできる場所は、特別な魅力があるはずだ。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2742
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_55577d7b:

    # hi "That's a good point. It's like this room gives you some kind of complete freedom."
    hi "それ、一理あるな。この部屋が、なんていうか完全な自由を与えてくれるって感じか"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2747
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_3959e7b8:

    # ha "Y-yeah."
    ha "う、うん"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2752
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_986a8c80:

    # ha "Say… do you play chess?"
    ha "あの……チェスってやりますか？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2754
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_45e08d8a:

    # hi "Chess? I've played it a bit, I guess."
    hi "チェス？　ちょっとくらいやってるかな"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2756
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_31ac7f79:

    # hi "I take it you've played before?"
    hi "ってことは、華子も前にやったことがあるんだ？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2761
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_98408389:

    # ha "A little…"
    ha "少し……"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2766
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_589b713e:

    # "Without saying anything more, Hanako moves to one of the cupboards and digs out a small chess set."
    "華子はそれ以上何も言わずに、戸棚に歩み寄ると、小さなチェスセットを探し出してくる。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2768
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_76fdd00e:

    # ha "Do… do you want…"
    ha "よ……よかったら……"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2770
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_8bce8989:

    # hi "Sure, why not?"
    hi "わかった、そうしようか"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2772
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_052f552e:

    # "I cut her off, but she doesn't seem to mind it."
    "遮ってしまったけど、華子は気にした風ではない。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2778
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_950bf2df:

    # "We arrange the pieces, and before long we are sending pawns charging to their inevitable fates."
    "俺たちは駒を並べ、やがてポーンを避けえない宿命へ向けて次々と突っ込ませる。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2780
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_3578e9f6:

    # "I take my time and intently examine each move and its consequences, nostalgia for the game taking second place to the matters at hand."
    "俺はじっくり時間をかけて、自分の指し手とその先の展開を検討する。その一方で、久々のチェスに懐かしさを感じてもいる。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2782
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_f15974f5:

    # "For a time the game is a lengthy battle of attrition, but I spot an opening and tear a line in her defense."
    "いっとき、ゲームは長ったらしい消耗戦に陥るものの、俺は華子の防御に隙間を見つけて、そこに一筋の切れ目を入れる。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2787
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_12ad9db2:

    # "A few moves later, her king is cornered by several of my pieces."
    "数手の後、華子のキングは俺の駒に追い詰められる。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2789
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_561bd533:

    # hi "Checkmate."
    hi "チェックメイト"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2791
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_eeefbc6b:

    # hi "You're not bad at this, are you?"
    hi "華子もなかなかやるじゃないか"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2793
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_247e43fb:

    # "An honest appraisal. Her technique is pretty good, but several times I was able to exploit her lack of prediction."
    "素直な褒め言葉だ。華子の腕前はかなりいい。だけどときどき俺は、その読みの隙をつくことができた。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2795
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_d2ecc5f4:

    # "I pick up a piece and examine it. It looks relatively new, yet worn for its age."
    "駒を一つ取り上げて観察する。比較的新しいけど、その割に使い込まれている。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2800
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_a2206eea:

    # ha "I… I guess not."
    ha "そ……そんなこと"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2802
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_90c3d178:

    # hi "Does Lilly play?"
    hi "リリーもやるのか？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2807
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_3c14a967:

    # "The absence of Hanako's answer causes me to think about my question."
    "華子の答えがないので、俺はこの質問について考え込む。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2809
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_987f38b1:

    # ha "A… A bit…"
    ha "す……少し……"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2811
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_adf0333f:

    # ha "T-this is the first time I've played against someone… other than her, or…"
    ha "リ、リリーたち以外の人とチェスをしたの、初めてなんです……一緒にしたことがあるのは、リリーと、それから……"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2816
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_5ee4defe:

    # "Or…?"
    "それから……？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2818
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_08373c7b:

    # "She cuts herself off abruptly, leaving the answer hanging in the air. Someone she knew before coming to Yamaku, maybe."
    "華子はあわてて口をつぐんでしまい、答えはわからないままだ。山久に来る前の知り合いなのかもしれない。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2820
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_632d8dd0:

    # hi "Well then, I'm honored to have played against you."
    hi "とにかく、相手してもらえて光栄だよ"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2825
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_e6f1f2e7:

    # ha "Um… can we play again?"
    ha "その……もう一回やりませんか？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2827
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_c7cae808:

    # "She asks as if she were asking me to cut off my own hands. The spirit of competition's gotten into her?"
    "まるで、俺に腕を切り落としてほしいとでもいうような頼み方だ。競争心に目覚めたんだろうか？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2829
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_f0409c1c:

    # hi "Sure. Though don't expect me to go easy on you this time…"
    hi "よし。けど、今度は手加減抜きで行くぞ……"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2831
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_4d509661:

    # "Not that I was before, mind. She seems to appreciate the competitive tone."
    "さっきも手加減なんてしてなかったんだけどな。華子は、俺の口調が挑戦的なことに気づいたようだ。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2836
translate jp a1_sunday_nc5xb3_fe1fb39b:

    # ha "S… same here…"
    ha "わ……私もです……"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2853
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_c34054ec:

    # "As we are setting up the pieces, there is a noise at the door."
    "俺たちが駒を並べていると、ドアが開く音がする。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2864
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_be82313e:

    # li "Good afternoon."
    li "こんにちは"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2871
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_eee002c4:

    # ha "Lilly…"
    ha "リリー……"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2873
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_1ed233ad:

    # hi "Oh, hey there Lilly. Are you finished?"
    hi "ああリリー、もう済んだのか？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2878
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_33ca3ef5:

    # li "You both are here? Wonderful. At any rate, our teacher managed to round up some extra help, so I was able to leave. Have you been here since you left?"
    li "二人ともここにいるんですか？　良かった。何はともあれ、先生が手伝いの人を集めてきてくれたので、抜けてこられました。あれからずっとここに？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2880
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_0200ab03:

    # hi "Pretty much, we've just been playing a bit of chess."
    hi "ほとんどね。ちょっとチェスをやっているところだよ"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2885
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_885decce:

    # ha "W-would you like a cup of tea?"
    ha "こ……紅茶いる？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2890
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_d936a0ba:

    # li "Actually, I think it may be a good idea to go outside for a little while…"
    li "実は、ちょっと外に出かけてみるのもいいんじゃないかと思ったんですけど……"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2895
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_8984c137:

    # "The instant drop in Hanako's face shows her objection to this plan, even though she says nothing."
    "華子はなにも言わないけど、たちまちその表情が落ち込むのを見れば、リリーの誘いに反対なのは明らかだ。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2897
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_94c8be61:

    # "I feel strangely compelled to voice what is plainly in view on her face, but Lilly can't see."
    "リリーには見えないけど、華子の顔にはっきりと浮かんでいる感情を伝えなくては、という奇妙な衝動に駆られる。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2899
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_6c2192f8:

    # hi "I… I kinda think that we should just stay here…"
    hi "あー……ここにいたほうがいいんじゃないかって思うな……"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2904
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_97537cd5:

    # li "Really? It's so crowded here that I was thinking we should leave the school and head for the local teahouse."
    li "そうですか？　ここはとても混んでいるから、学校を出て近くの喫茶店に行った方がいいかと思っていたんです"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2909
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_ceaba2eb:

    # ha "You mean the S-Shanghai?"
    ha "し、上海のこと？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2914
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_2de7eece:

    # li "Of course; with everyone at the festival it should be practically empty."
    li "はい、もちろん。町の人も山久の生徒も、みなさん学園祭に来ているのできっと空いていると思いますよ"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2916
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_ac86271c:

    # hi "Teahouse?"
    hi "喫茶店？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2921
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_f8c832f7:

    # li "Oh, that's right, you probably don't know of it."
    li "あら、そうでした。たぶん久夫さんは知らないでしょうね"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2926
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_43ea994d:

    # li "There is a teahouse not far from here, which we go to every so often."
    li "この近くに私たちが時々行く喫茶店があるんです"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2928
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_9a2d8685:

    # hi "Sounds like a plan. Hanako, what do you think?"
    hi "よさそうだな。華子、どう思う？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2936
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_4210c793:

    # "Hanako jumps a little at being forced into the conversation, but at least she seems less distraught than before."
    "話を振られて華子が少し飛び上がる。だけど少なくともさっきよりはうろたえていないようだ。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2941
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_186391c4:

    # ha "If… if it's the Shanghai, I think it'll be nice."
    ha "し……上海ならいいかな"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2946
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_726c4283:

    # li "Well then, it's settled. Let's be on our way."
    li "では決まりですね。行きましょうか"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2951
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_9b5991a9:

    # "Hanako and I rise from the table and our preempted chess game."
    "華子と俺はチェスをやめ、テーブルから立ち上がる。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2953
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_d42ef27f:

    # "Before I can do anything, Hanako has poured the pieces into a small container and placed the board away."
    "俺がなにかしようとするまえに、華子が駒を小さな入れ物に流し込むように入れて、盤を片付けてしまう。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2955
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_1194027a:

    # hi "Looks like we're ready now. Please, lead on."
    hi "準備はできたな。じゃあ案内してよ"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2968
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_bc1b3da4:

    # "Hanako moves to Lilly's side and we venture onto the school's corridors."
    "華子がリリーの隣に移動し、俺たちは廊下へと冒険の旅に漕ぎ出す。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2977
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_f0f0f736:

    # "The pair leads me through a series of unfamiliar doors, and we emerge on the side of the building opposite of the festival grounds."
    "二人は見覚えのないいくつものドアを通って俺を先導し、学園祭が行われているグラウンドの反対側の建物の脇へと出た。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2979
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_71f3b542:

    # "Insulated by the heavy stone of the building, the noise from the crowd has faded to a murmur."
    "建物の重い石材に遮られ、人混みの喧騒はざわめき程度の大きさにしか聞こえない。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2981
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_4e65537f:

    # hi "Strange; I thought that most people would be beginning to leave by now…"
    hi "変だな、みんなもう帰り始めているだろうと思ったけど……"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2989
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_0dc02169:

    # li "They're probably here to view the fireworks."
    li "あの方々はたぶん花火を見るためにここにいるんでしょう"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2991
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_0b36e291:

    # hi "Fireworks?"
    hi "花火？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2996
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_4a3ffb93:

    # li "Yes, apparently the school puts on quite a show. A lot of people come from town just to watch them."
    li "はい、どうやら学校が盛大なショーをするらしいですよ。花火を見るためだけに、街から大勢の人が来るんです"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:2998
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_2609725b:

    # "Lilly's decision to leave the school grounds seems to make sense now. Hanako would probably have a hard time with the whole town descending onto the school. Or ascending, as the case may be."
    "リリーが学校を出ると決めた理由が今理解できた。町全体の人が学校になだれ込んでくれば、華子にとっては辛いことだろう。この場合『逆流してくる』が正しいかもしれないけど。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3006
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_40d96c46:

    # "For the second time since arriving at Yamaku I find myself walking down this road with Lilly."
    "リリーと一緒にこの道を下るのは山久に来てから２回目だ。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3008
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_39abfb00:

    # "Only now that I can barely hear the incessant noise of the festival do I realize how loud it was. I can hear my ears ringing slightly in the still evening air as they recover from the day's assault on them."
    "今になって絶え間ない学園祭の騒音がかすかに聞こえてきて、やっとその騒々しさに気がつく。昼間の音の攻撃から耳が回復してくるとともに、静かな夕方の空気の中で、わずかに耳なりが聞こえる。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3016
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_8ef8fbf8:

    # "Hanako clings to Lilly, but still manages to guide her along the road. That, and avoiding the occasional gaze from curious pedestrians, appears to completely sap her constitution."
    "華子はリリーにぴったりとくっつきながらも道に従ってリリーのガイドを務めている。それに加えて歩行者からの好奇の視線を避けているうちに、彼女から活気がすっかり失われていく。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3018
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_cf4c2777:

    # "She rarely raises her focus from the ground in front of her, nor does she utter a word."
    "華子はめったに地面から顔を上げず、一言もしゃべらない。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3020
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_fa3136a6:

    # "Lilly, on the other hand, maintains her prim and proper persona just as she does in school. It's obvious she purposely puts effort into her appearance, rather than hiding it as Hanako does."
    "一方でリリーはまさに学校にいるときのように礼儀正しく上品な外見を崩さないでいる。華子のように隠すのではなく、あえて自分の見た目を保つよう努めているのは明らかだ。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3022
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_f8dca8a3:

    # "It's striking how different they are in their way of holding themselves outside of Yamaku's grounds. That said, it's obvious in both their cases that they do visibly change."
    "学校の外での二人の振る舞いがこんなに違うことに驚く。とはいっても、どちらの振る舞いも明らかに目に見えて変わっている。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3026
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_76b2fe88:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3032
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_6c50a58e:

    # n "{vspace=90}Inside Yamaku, everyone is 'special,' which negates the 'special-ness' of it."
    n "\n\n\n山久学園ではみんなが『特別』で、それは『特別』であることの『特別さ』を打ち消している。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3034
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_3889aadd:

    # n "But once we venture outside the school gates, we are returned to the status of 'outsider' and generic labels."
    n "だけど一度校門の外に踏み出せば、俺たちは『部外者』という身分に、ひとくくりにされるような肩書きに戻ってしまう。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3036
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_1e896e9d:

    # n "Especially when we are still in school uniform. It's like hanging a sign around your neck challenging people to figure out what is wrong with you."
    n "制服を着たままの時はなおさらだ。『どこが悪いか当ててみな』という看板を首にぶら下げているようなものだ。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3038
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_716f1f1e:

    # n "I'm surprised that so many of the students keep it on. Then again, with canes and wheelchairs common among the students, I guess it's not really that much of a giveaway."
    n "制服を着たままの生徒がこんなにたくさんいることに驚く。でも山久の生徒にとって杖や車椅子が珍しくないことを考えれば、制服くらい大したことではないのかもしれない。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3040
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_7f115645:

    # n "{vspace=30}Or maybe I'm the only one that sees this as a stigma? Maybe you get used to it after a time, like any other school uniform."
    n "\nそれとも、これを不名誉な代物として見ているのはもしかして俺だけなのか？　しばらくすれば他の学校の制服のように慣れるのだろうか。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3046
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_76b2fe88_1:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3051
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_26cf3622:

    # "The teahouse seems fairly standard from the outside; just an ordinary building with typical signs decorating the entrance."
    "案内された喫茶店は外から見る分には極めて普通のようだ。よくありがちな感じの看板で入口が装飾された平凡な建物である。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3053
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_27d2f2f8:

    # "It looks like the type of place you'd walk by without a thought, just another generic café in a sea of thousands."
    "それは何の気なしに通り過ぎるであろう場所、どこにでもありそうな普通のカフェでしかない。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3055
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_6bc4afea:

    # "If Hanako hadn't steered Lilly into the entrance I would have continued on down the road without ever knowing that it existed."
    "もし華子がリリーを入口の中へと導いていなければ、俺は建物の存在にすら気づかずに道を下っていただろう。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3066
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_47981cff:

    # "Inside the teahouse it takes on a more traditional feel. Everything seems to have been made from the same lump of timber, from the counter and benches to the high-backed booths around the walls."
    "喫茶店の中は昔ながらな感じが漂っている。カウンターや座席から壁際の高い仕切りで仕切られた席まで、店の中にあるもの全てが同じ木材から作られているようだ。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3068
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_dd78b4c4:

    # "But the most striking feature of the room is the lack of life. I think I can faintly hear something bubbling away in the background, but otherwise the room is silent."
    "だけどこの部屋の最も印象的な特徴は、人のいる感じがしないことだ。裏のほうでなにかが沸騰している音がかすかに聞こえる気がするけど、それ以外は無音だ。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3070
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_ef442f8c:

    # "Without any direction, we simply wait near the entrance, politely obeying the 'Please wait to be seated' sign."
    "どうするわけでもなく、俺たちは礼儀正しく『席に座らずにお待ちください』という看板に従いつつ入口付近でただ待つ。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3072
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_2a721a68:

    # hi "Er, is this place closed or something?"
    hi "あれ、やってないのかな？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3086
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_5d85304a:

    # "The sound of a chair falling over echoes throughout the empty room, and a head shoots up from inside a booth."
    "椅子が倒れる音が誰もいない部屋に響き、仕切り席の中から頭が飛び出す。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3093
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_fc984c6d:

    # yu "I wasn't asleep and welcome to the Shanghai!"
    yu "ねっ寝てないですよ、いらっしゃいませ！"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3095
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_5738ec83:

    # "Yuuko, dressed in a pastel apron and clutching a menu, rushes to greet us. Her misaligned glasses and ruffled hair cast suspicion on her previous statement."
    "パステルカラーのエプロンを着てメニューを握りしめた優子さんが、もの凄い勢いで俺たちを出迎える。彼女のズレた眼鏡と乱れた髪の毛がさっきの言葉への疑いを呼び起こす。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3097
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_7cc94470:

    # "But whether she was asleep or not isn't the first question that leaps to my mind."
    "しかし彼女が居眠りをしていたかどうか以上に気になることがある。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3099
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_e090f735:

    # hi "You work here now? What happened to the library?"
    hi "ここで働いているんですか？　図書室はどうしたんです？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3104
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_b1f0294c:

    # yu "What? Lilly? Hisao?"
    yu "えっ？　リリー？　中井くん？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3109
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_0317a797:

    # yu "Welcome to the Shanghai!"
    yu "ようこそ、上海へ！"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3122
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_acd01465:

    # "Yuuko, still waking up, jerks into a violent bow, dislodging her glasses in the process."
    "まだ半分寝ている優子さんが急に荒っぽいおじぎをすると、彼女の眼鏡が落っこちてしまう。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3124
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_3d6041db:

    # yu "Uweh!? My glasses…"
    yu "うひゃぁ！？　私の眼鏡……"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3126
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_c9a1d76f:

    # "As I pick up her spectacles off the floor, Lilly offers an explanation."
    "俺が床から眼鏡を拾ってあげると、リリーが説明してくれる。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3135
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_5d91fdb3:

    # li "Yuuko works here part-time as well as at the library. It's one of the reasons we like to come here."
    li "優子さんは図書室と同じようにここでアルバイトをされているんです。私たちがここに来るのが好きな理由の一つですね"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3140
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_c081a803:

    # "Yuuko takes her glasses from my hands, shakily putting them back on."
    "優子さんは俺から眼鏡を受け取り、おぼつかない手つきでかけ直す。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3142
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_c7a0a95b:

    # yu "Yes… that's right… thanks…"
    yu "うん……そう……ありがとう……"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3147
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_816c3178:

    # yu "Shall I show you to your table?"
    yu "テーブルまで案内しましょうか？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3152
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_d80beb12:

    # yu "There's no-one else here so you can choose your table and order whatever you like, but there may be a delay as I will have to make it myself…"
    yu "他に誰もいないから、好きなところに座ってなんでも注文してね。私が作らないといけないから遅くなっちゃうかもしれないけど……"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3157
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_1c307b6d:

    # li "It's all right, Yuuko. Just a pot of black tea and a plate of sandwiches will be fine."
    li "大丈夫です、優子さん。紅茶とサンドイッチでいいです"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3162
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_c6e8da86:

    # yu "Right! I'll get right onto that!"
    yu "それだわ！　すぐに作るね！"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3171
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_ac44f06a:

    # "Yuuko hurries off to the back of the café, leaving us still standing at the entrance."
    "優子さんは入口に突っ立っている俺たちを残して厨房へと消えていく。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3173
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_2979573b:

    # "She pushes the swinging half-doors open before realizing that she hasn't seated us."
    "彼女は厨房のドアを開けたところで俺たちをまだ席へ案内していないことに気づく。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3175
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_e00fb94b:

    # yu "I'm sorry! I'm sorry! Please, sit wherever you'd like! I'll be right back!"
    yu "ごめん、ごめんね！　どこでも好きなところに座って！　すぐに戻ってくるから！"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3185
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_f29a27e8:

    # "Following her advice, I lead Lilly to the nearest booth as Hanako follows."
    "彼女に促され、俺はリリーを一番近い仕切り席へと連れて行き、それに華子も続く。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3202
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_a0c5543b:

    # "As I begin to sit next to Lilly, I realize how appropriate this place is for Hanako."
    "リリーの隣に腰を下ろすと、俺はこの場所がどれだけ華子に適しているかということを実感する。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3204
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_848c0fde:

    # "The high-backed booths totally separate you from the rest of the room, and it doesn't look like it gets all that many customers."
    "背の高い仕切りを持つ仕切り席は、店の他の場所から完全に隔たっていて、加えてそんなに多くの客が入れるようにも見えない。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3206
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_a9654a20:

    # "All of the furnishings, from the cushions on the benches to the condiment holders, look dated but aren't overly worn."
    "座席の上のクッションから調味料入れまで全ての家具が旧式に見えるけど、そこまで古臭い感じはしない。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3208
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_7fb7f71f:

    # "I wonder if Lilly deliberately selects places like this to take Hanako? She seems like the type that would go to lengths to cater to Hanako's unique predicament."
    "リリーは華子を連れてくるためにあえてこのような場所を選ぶのだろうか？　彼女は華子の置かれた独特な苦境に合う条件を満たすためならどんな苦労もいとわない人間のようだ。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3215
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_5f1419e3:

    # li "So, Hisao, I didn't know you played chess…"
    li "そういえば、久夫さん。あなたがチェスをやっていたなんて知りませんでした……"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3217
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_534713e9:

    # hi "Well, not very well, but I do know how to play."
    hi "ああ、上手くはないけどね。やり方くらいは知ってるよ"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3222
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_bf522883:

    # li "I suppose the obvious question would now be… who won?"
    li "ありきたりの質問でしょうけど……どちらが勝ったんですか？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3224
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_75cfb0bd:

    # "Lilly's innocent smile makes me hesitate. I don't really want to look like I'm lording my victory over Hanako."
    "リリーの無邪気な微笑みを見て、俺は口ごもってしまう。華子に勝ちを自慢するようには見られたくない。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3229
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_a7fc18fa:

    # ha "H-Hisao did."
    ha "ひ……久夫くん"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3231
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_3db8419f:

    # hi "Yes… but, uh, not by much…"
    hi "うん……まあ、なんとかね……"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3233
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_26918f89:

    # "Damn. Saying that out loud makes me feel like I've done something terrible."
    "なにやってんだ。声に出すと同時に俺は後悔の念に駆られる。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3238
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_bf8dfb0f:

    # li "Well done, Hisao. You've accomplished something I've only ever failed at."
    li "やりましたね、久夫さん。あなたは私が未だにできないことを成し遂げてしまいました"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3240
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_f38e6fec:

    # hi "Er, thanks. I haven't played in ages, so it felt good to play again."
    hi "えっと、ありがとう。長いあいだやってなかったから、またできてよかったよ"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3245
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_0f6f54af:

    # ha "Y… yes… It did."
    ha "う……うん……そうだね"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3247
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_94d3f473:

    # "Hanako fidgets with her hair a little and looks away as she replies, but a small smile emerges."
    "華子は目を合わさずに髪をいじくりながら答える。しかしその顔にはわずかに笑みが浮かんでいる。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3249
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_83f25d54:

    # "It's a little more extreme of a reaction than I expected, but still kind of cute in that Hanako way."
    "それは俺の予想をはるかに超えた反応だったけど、華子らしくてなんだかかわいいと思えてくる。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3267
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_1aaa0d7d:

    # "It throws me a little off guard, and only Yuuko's cataclysmic re-entry shocks me back into conversation."
    "俺がそんな華子の反応に不意を打たれていると、大変動が起こるかのような優子さんの再登場によって会話へと引き戻される。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3269
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_9d3f1306:

    # hi "Are you all right there, Yuuko? Do you need a hand?"
    hi "大丈夫ですか？　優子さん。手伝いましょうか？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3275
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_71cc8473:

    # yu "I'm fine I'm fine I'm fine. I have to do this properly, it's my job."
    yu "大丈夫、大丈夫よっ大丈夫っっ……私の仕事なんだからちゃんと自分でやらないと……"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3280
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_0b81c00c:

    # "Concentration plays across her face while she stares at the tray in her hands, as if simply looking at its contents will hold them in place."
    "手に持っているトレイを睨みつける彼女の顔には、トレイの中身を凝視すれば中身はその場に留まるだろうというかのように集中している表情が浮かんでいる。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3285
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_b3873f3a:

    # "Sadly, this doesn't prove all that effective; the cups and saucers slowly dance around, occasionally clattering as they collide with one another."
    "悲しいかな、そんな効果はあるはずもなく、カップとソーサーが時折互いにぶつかってカタカタと音を立てながらゆっくりと跳ね回る。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3294
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_27837391:

    # "Taking great care, Yuuko sets the tray down on the table with only the subtlest of crashes."
    "細心の注意を払いながら、優子さんがほとんど音を立てずにトレイをテーブルに置く。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3299
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_511427b5:

    # yu "There, see!"
    yu "ほら、できた！"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3301
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_9bfe88dc:

    # hi "Er, well done?"
    hi "えっと、よくできました……でいいのかな？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3306
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_bcfc619d:

    # li "Thank you, Yuuko."
    li "ありがとうございます、優子さん"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3317
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_13b1b2e9:

    # "Yuuko's head rockets downwards in her distinctive bow before answering."
    "優子さんは頭を思いっきり振りおろす特徴的なおじぎをしてから返事をする。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3322
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_35facfb4:

    # yu "You're very welcome."
    yu "どういたしましてっ！！"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3327
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_25256784:

    # li "Would you like to join us? There's something else I'd like to discuss about that recent order, if I may…"
    li "よければ優子さんもご一緒にどうですか？　この前の発注について、他にも相談したいことがあるんですが……"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3329
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_b8c5ae0a:

    # "Ah, that's right. Lilly and Yuuko were discussing a pile of books when I first met Hanako."
    "ああ、そうだ。俺が初めて華子に会ったときにリリーと優子さんはたくさんの本について話し合っていたっけ。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3331
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_4881d85e:

    # "Something about Lilly helping with the Braille…"
    "点字の本のことでリリーが手伝う、とかなんとか……"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3336
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_c5ef5938:

    # yu "Ah… yes. We didn't get the chance to go through them, did we?"
    yu "あー……うん。話す機会がなかったね"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3342
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_fa46b2a5:

    # "Yuuko hastily sits down next to Hanako."
    "優子さんは慌てて華子の隣に座る。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3344
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_f06b8f5a:

    # "Apparently her dedication to this job only goes as far as her concentration; once it is broken, she suddenly loses it."
    "どうやら優子さんの仕事熱心さは、集中力が残っている間しか続かないようだ。集中が途切れると、仕事も放り出してしまう。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3349
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_52e54e36:

    # yu "I'll be in the library tomorrow afternoon if you'd like to try again…"
    yu "また話をするんだったら、明日の午後は図書室にいるけど……"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3354
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_dceb800f:

    # li "That sounds perfect, I'll meet you there after classes."
    li "ちょうどいいですね。授業が終わったら伺います"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3359
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_966b04cf:

    # ha "Um… L-Lilly…"
    ha "あの……り、リリー……"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3364
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_e9d84f6a:

    # li "Oh dear, that's right. Tomorrow is Monday, how could I have forgotten?"
    li "あら、そうでした。明日は月曜日でしたね。どうして忘れてたんでしょう"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3366
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_0c2a2ff6:

    # "I'm starting to feel a little left out of the loop here. Then again that's to be expected; I have been here for barely a week, so it's impossible to know everyone's schedule."
    "なんだか会話に置いて行かれている気がしてくる。とはいっても、当たり前だ。ここに来てからまだ間もないのだから、全ての人の予定を知ることなんて不可能だ。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3371
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_e65685a8:

    # li "Well, perhaps we could come to some other arrangement."
    li "そうですね、他の日に図書室に行くという選択肢もありますからね"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3376
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_c2cd1e86:

    # li "Yuuko, will you be in the library later in the week?"
    li "優子さん、今週中は図書室にいますか？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3381
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_53f45b5f:

    # yu "Hmm, maybe, but this is already overdue…"
    yu "うーん……たぶん、でももう先延ばしにするのは厳しいかも……"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3386
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_a7f0abb8:

    # ha "A-and there are some… things I n-need…"
    ha "わ、私も……どうしても必要なものが……あって……"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3391
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_026ce1fe:

    # li "This might be a problem…"
    li "これは困りましたね……"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3393
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_c16e48e2:

    # "Lilly ponders for a second before discovering the answer."
    "リリーは少しのあいだ考えを巡らせ、答えを見つける。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3398
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_2c3ad4c7:

    # li "I wonder, might we be able to enlist the help of another, if need be…?"
    li "できたら、残りのお一方の助けを借りられないでしょうか？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3400
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_8879c33d:

    # hi "Um, to do what? You lost me quite some time ago…"
    hi "えっ、何をするって？　ずいぶん前から話について行ってないんだけど……"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3402
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_0ce2af3e:

    # "Being volunteered for something without even having the slightest idea what is going on isn't really my thing."
    "状況がさっぱりわからない状態でなにか手伝わされる、というのはあまり気に入らない。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3404
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_15918ee0:

    # "And here I thought I had finally escaped the clutches of the Student Council and their repeated attempts to recruit me."
    "こっちはやっとのことで生徒会の魔の手と、あいつらの度重なる勧誘から逃れられたと思っていたのに。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3409
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_745607ca:

    # li "Oh, of course. The other day I was helping Yuuko sort the new Braille books in the library."
    li "ああ、そうでした。先日、優子さんの手伝いで、図書室の点字本の整理をしていたんです"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3414
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_ca748634:

    # li "But Hanako and I usually go shopping on Monday afternoons; it's quieter on that day than on weekends."
    li "でも華ちゃんと私は月曜日の午後はいつもお買いものに出かけるんです。そのほうが週末よりも混んでいないんですよ"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3416
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_91b29a8e:

    # li "Last week we couldn't go because I was busy with the festival. I managed to slip away later in the week, but Hanako couldn't make it."
    li "先週は私が学園祭の準備で忙しかったので行けなかったんです。その後なら時間を作ることができたので日を改めようとしたのですが、先週中はそれ以降華ちゃんの予定が合わなくて"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3418
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_c3cce205:

    # hi "Well, since I can't read Braille, I'm assuming you'd like me to go shopping with Hanako?"
    hi "なるほど。俺は点字は読めないから、華子と買いものに行ってほしいってこと？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3424
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_f3049004:

    # li "Correct. You were a great help to me the other day."
    li "はい。先日はとても助かりましたし"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3426
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_e11f82f9:

    # hi "I think I can handle that. Hanako, what do you think?"
    hi "俺は大丈夫だと思うよ。華子はどう？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3431
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_f8074f93:

    # ha "I-if you wouldn't mind…"
    ha "ひ、久夫くんが嫌じゃなければ……"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3433
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_f88aa085:

    # hi "Of course not. I'm still not familiar with all the stores in the area, so it sounds like a good idea."
    hi "もちろん嫌じゃないよ。俺はまだこの地域の店に詳しくないからいいアイディアだと思う"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3438
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_57db572d:

    # ha "O-okay."
    ha "う、うん、いいよ"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3443
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_f5fb1474:

    # li "Now that we have that arranged, shall we have some tea?"
    li "決まりですね。紅茶、飲みませんか？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3445
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_ee8376eb:

    # "It's now that I realize our tea has been sitting idly by all this time, getting no hotter."
    "先ほど出された紅茶が口をつけられないままで冷えてしまっていることに今気づく。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3450
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_ed7be484:

    # yu "It's my fault! Let me pour that for you…"
    yu "私のせいだ！　もう一回入れさせて……"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3452
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_d073dc19:

    # "Yuuko reaches out with shaking hands, but I intercept her; she looks in no state to be handling hot liquids."
    "優子さんが手を小刻みに震わせながら伸ばしてくる。しかし俺はこれを遮る。今の彼女は熱い液体を扱える状態にあるようには見えない。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3454
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_0651b30f:

    # hi "It's all right, I've got it. Since you've already made the tea and sandwiches, you've fulfilled your waitress duties, right?"
    hi "大丈夫ですよ、僕がやりますから。あなたは紅茶を入れてサンドイッチを作ってくれました。これでもうウェイトレスとしての義務は果たしたでしょう？　ね？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3459
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_93bfe294:

    # yu "I… I guess."
    yu "そ……そうね"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3461
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_4fd2aefb:

    # "Yuuko relaxes a little, but still watches eagerly as I share out the assortment."
    "優子さんは少しは落ち着いたけど、俺が料理を各々に振り分けているあいだ、まだ熱心な眼差しを注いでくる。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3472
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_95291c6a:

    # "As I am about to bite into the sandwich, a low, loud rumble can be heard, along with a flash of light from outside."
    "俺がサンドイッチにかぶりつこうとしたとき、低く大きなドーンという音が聞こえ、ほぼ同時に外から閃光が差し込む。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3479
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_1ce96251:

    # li "Ah, I take it the show has started."
    li "あら、始まりましたね"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3486
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_6243b9e5:

    # "Only now looking outside, I realize that dusk has come and gone, leaving us in the peak of twilight."
    "外を見てやっと気づいたけど、太陽はとっくに沈んでしまっていて、夕焼けの薄明かりだけが残っている。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3488
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_51fc9770:

    # "Sparking tracers arc upwards ready to explode in the floral shapes of fireworks."
    "閃光を放つ火の玉が花の形に爆発しようと天に昇っていく。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3496
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_652b3dc3:

    # yu "Let's go watch!"
    yu "見に行こうよ！"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3501
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_8fb2f064:

    # yu "Oh… sorry Lilly…"
    yu "あ……ごめんなさい、リリー……"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3513
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_3d9071b3:

    # li "Please, don't miss the show on my account. From what I've heard, this isn't a bad location to watch them from."
    li "私にはかまわないで見てきてください。音を聞いた限り、ここは花火を見るには悪くない場所のようですね"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3524
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_6f890264:

    # "With the exception of Lilly, we rush to the window of the small teahouse to watch the show."
    "リリーを除いた三人は花火を見るために小さな喫茶店の窓に駆け寄る。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3526
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_d40bd6fd:

    # "The strobe of colored lights plays across Hanako and Yuuko's smiling faces, and for a second I forget to look out the window."
    "様々な色の光が華子と優子さんの笑顔のあちこちで揺れ動ているのを見て、少しのあいだ俺は窓の外を見ることを忘れてしまう。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3528
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_2c17e195:

    # "In this totally new world, there are a few things that don't change."
    "こんなまったく新しい世界でも、変わらないものが少しはある。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3530
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_4513c5a0:

    # "I think that's why the school makes such a fuss over this festival. It's a chance to show the similarities between everyone."
    "それが山久学園が学園祭でこんなお祭り騒ぎを起こす理由なんだと思う。この笑顔のように誰にでも似通ったところがある、ということを示す機会なんだ。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3537
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_434f301c:

    # "The show is over all too quickly; fireworks are expensive, even for the most well-funded schools."
    "ショーはあっという間に終わってしまう。もっとも潤沢な予算がある学校にとっても、花火というのは高価なものなのだ。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3542
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_eb7bb07f:

    # "Before we return to our tea and sandwiches, Hanako turns to me."
    "食事に戻るまえに華子がこちらを向く。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3547
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_cdacd300:

    # ha "Um, t-thanks for today."
    ha "き、きょうはありがとう"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3552
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_2c7b3fa6:

    # ha "…and tomorrow."
    ha "……それと、明日も……"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3554
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_a747b41a:

    # hi "That's okay; I don't think that I could have faced those crowds either."
    hi "いいって。俺もあの人混みには耐えられなかったと思うし"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3556
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_9a09cac5:

    # hi "On days like this it's more relaxing to spend some time away from everyone, don't you think?"
    hi "今日みたいにみんなから離れて過ごすのって落ち着くよな。そう思わない？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3561
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_3959e7b8:

    # ha "Y-yeah."
    ha "う、うん"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3563
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_d91582b4:

    # hi "Anyway, we've been delaying this tea for far too long now, let's get back."
    hi "ところで、ずいぶんと紅茶をほったらかしてるし、戻ろうか"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3568
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_ff70d1cd:

    # ha "S-sure."
    ha "う、うん"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3591
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_8ba50e80:

    # "We return to the booth and our light meal."
    "俺たちは席に戻り、食事を再開する。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3596
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_a0d041c7:

    # li "That sounded impressive. Bigger than last year's at least."
    li "あの音は印象的ですね。少なくとも去年よりも大きいです"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3601
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_d60e5974:

    # yu "Yeah it was great! I've never seen them put on such a show."
    yu "うん！　すごかったね！　こんなショー見たことないよ"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3603
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_cc132f25:

    # yu "It gets better every year!"
    yu "年を重ねるごとに良くなってる！"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3608
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_00d23be2:

    # li "I'm afraid, however, that during that time, the tea has gone cold."
    li "ですが、見ているあいだに紅茶がまた冷えてしまったみたいです"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3615
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_00c5d1e3:

    # yu "Oh no! Let me make some more! This is my fault!"
    yu "やだ！　もう一度作らせて！　私のせいだわ！"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3617
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_7e845234:

    # hi "Calm down, Yuuko, it's nobody's fault."
    hi "落ち着いてください、優子さん。誰のせいでもないですよ"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3619
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_713396ae:

    # "I take a sip from my cup, just to prove the point."
    "俺はそれを証明するために自分のカップを一口すする。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3621
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_3460f5d5:

    # hi "This tea isn't too bad cool, anyway. It's like an iced tea."
    hi "とにかく、この紅茶、冷たくてもまあまあおいしいですから。アイスティーみたいで"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3626
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_68d170e9:

    # yu "Really?"
    yu "本当？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3628
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_584cd9e4:

    # hi "Yes, really. If you add a bit of sugar it's kinda nice."
    hi "はい、本当です。砂糖を少し入れればいい感じですね"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3633
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_5d08e4a4:

    # yu "Are you sure?"
    yu "本当に本当？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3635
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_f24885aa:

    # hi "I'm positive. Now why don't you sit down and we'll finish this together?"
    hi "本当ですって。座って一緒に食べませんか？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3640
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_669791aa:

    # yu "O-okay."
    yu "う、うん"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3646
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_c4c01574:

    # "Yuuko doesn't seem convinced, but sits down regardless."
    "優子さんは疑っているようだけど、とりあえず腰を下ろす。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3648
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_1690904f:

    # "She carefully measures out about five teaspoons of sugar and adds them to her tea."
    "彼女は注意深くティースプーン五杯分の砂糖を測り取り、紅茶に入れる。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3650
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_9f133c3d:

    # hi "Er, I said a bit of sugar…"
    hi "あのー、俺は少しって言ったはずですけど……"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3655
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_30bc445e:

    # yu "I know but I like my tea sweet anyway."
    yu "わかってるよ。でも私は甘いほうが好きなの"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3657
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_953c874d:

    # "Curiously I peer into her cup. As expected, hardly any of the sugar dissolves in the cold liquid."
    "興味をそそられて、優子さんのカップをのぞき込む。案の定、冷たい液体の中では砂糖はほとんど溶けていない。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3659
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_978ab7b4:

    # "She stirs it twice before upturning the cup and drinking the contents, sugar and all, in a single mouthful."
    "彼女は二回ほどかき混ぜるとカップを傾け、溶け残っている砂糖まで一口で飲み干してしまう。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3664
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_7694c86c:

    # yu "You're right! That's not bad at all!"
    yu "本当だ！　すごくおいしいわ！"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3666
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_f00abd9e:

    # hi "Er, good…"
    hi "えっと……それは良かったですね"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3668
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_e5378a2f:

    # "I look back to Lilly and Hanako, both of whom have finished their meal as I witnessed Yuuko's personality in action."
    "リリーと華子に視線を戻す。二人とも俺が優子さんの個性的な行動を見ているあいだに食事を終えてしまったようだ。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3670
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_dc97c8ab:

    # "Not wanting to hold anyone up, I use her tactic and finish the remainder of my tea in a single swill."
    "みんなを待たせたくないので、俺は優子さんと同じように紅茶の残りを一息に飲み干す。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3672
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_e99c457b:

    # hi "Well then, it seems we're all finished."
    hi "さて、みんな食べ終わったみたいだな"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3677
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_d4addad6:

    # li "Should we head back now or do we want seconds?"
    li "帰りますか？　それともおかわりをいただきましょうか？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3682
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_9fbba49f:

    # "Yuuko's expression shows that this is quite clearly not a good idea."
    "優子さんの表情を見るに、間違いなくそれはやめておいたほうがよさそうだ。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3684
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_84ff9f73:

    # hi "I think that it would be best if we got back soon."
    hi "すぐ帰るのが一番良いんじゃないかな"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3686
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_faab51b2:

    # hi "We do have to get back before curfew, after all."
    hi "やっぱり、門限までには帰らないといけないし"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3691
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_ed2213e5:

    # li "Oh, that is a good point."
    li "あ、それは大事ですね"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3696
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_2a33b967:

    # li "I'll meet you tomorrow, Yuuko."
    li "また明日お会いしましょう、優子さん"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3701
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_5a5a996d:

    # yu "I'll be looking forward to it, Lilly. Goodbye, everyone."
    yu "うん待ってるね、リリー。じゃあね、みんな"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3711
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_57fe8a62:

    # "We make our way out of the small teahouse and into the dark of the night."
    "俺たちは小さな喫茶店から出て夜の闇へと進んでいく。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3717
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_24b82e31:

    # "Lilly and Hanako once again take point, but under the cover of darkness Hanako seems slightly less stressed than she did on the trip here."
    "リリーと華子はまた先頭に立つ。でも宵闇の中では、華子はここにくるときと比べてほんの少しだけ気が楽そうに見える。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3719
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_4661f8a0:

    # "We move against the occasional group of people emptying the school grounds, but Hanako seems to lead us along a few minor roads, avoiding the bulk of the crowd."
    "時折、学校のグラウンドから出てきた人たちの集団に出会いながら進む。しかし華子は大規模な人混みを避けるために裏道を案内しているようだ。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3726
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_75df3554:

    # "Outside the dorms, the school seems strangely quiet when compared to the noise of the day."
    "寮の前まで来ると、学校が昼間の喧騒に比べて奇妙なほど静まり返っているように感じられる。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3728
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_cb0b3142:

    # hi "Well then, thank you both for today. I think I learned a lot."
    hi "さて、二人とも今日はありがとう。色々わかった気がするよ"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3736
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_7ef1c6f7:

    # li "You're most welcome, but I'm afraid that I really must be going. Today's been a long day."
    li "どういたしまして。でももう帰らないと。今日は長い一日でしたから"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3738
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_ac935e94:

    # "That's right; Lilly spent all of today on her feet, and I can imagine that walking outside of the school would be pretty tiring for her."
    "そうだった。リリーは一日ずっと立ちっぱなしだったし、学校の外に出ることでとても疲れただろうことも想像がつく。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3740
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_e37b09b4:

    # "I feel a pang of guilt as I remember that I was probably the only one in the school that got up around ten this morning."
    "今朝十時ごろに起きた人間はたぶん自分だけだろうということを思い起こし、俺は罪悪感に駆られる。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3742
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_0527a675:

    # hi "Sure thing."
    hi "じゃあ遠慮なく"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3744
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_efbc00b4:

    # hi "Well, I'll see you both tomorrow. Good night."
    hi "じゃあ、また明日な。おやすみ"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3749
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_5606c1a8:

    # li "Good night, Hisao."
    li "おやすみなさい、久夫さん"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3754
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_f2bb6c69:

    # ha "N… night."
    ha "お……おやすみ"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3760
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_d6117fd4:

    # "The girls return to their dorm, and I to mine."
    "二人は寮へと戻っていき、俺も自分の寮へと帰る。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3762
translate jp a1_sunday_movement_45cfedb2:

    # "Actually, now that I consider it, today tired me out as well."
    "……確かに、考えてみると今日は俺も疲れたな。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3777
translate jp a1_sunday_throwing_balls_63839cf5:

    # hi "I'm going to have to hang out with the Student Council, since I lost a bet."
    hi "生徒会のやつらに付き合わないといけないんだ。賭けに負けちゃってさ"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3779
translate jp a1_sunday_throwing_balls_44ec0c0f:

    # "I realize that we didn't agree on when and where. I'll just wait for them rather than risk us missing each other in the chaos outside. They must be busy running around and organizing things, anyway."
    "そういえば、いつどこで待ち合わせるか決めていなかった。外の混雑で行き違いになりそうなので、ここであいつらを待つことにする。どうせ二人とも、運営であちこち走り回って忙しいだろうし。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3781
translate jp a1_sunday_throwing_balls_b860a369:

    # "It's funny. I would've assumed the price for losing to Shizune in her stupid game to be a lot more severe. This is just a pretense for spending time with her. In that case, I guess she just wants me to have fun."
    "不思議なもんだ。あんな馬鹿げた勝負で静音に負けた代償はずっと高くつくと思ったのに。これは俺が静音と一緒に過ごすための口実でしかないんだ。だとしたら、あいつは俺に楽しんで欲しいだけなんだろうな。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3783
translate jp a1_sunday_throwing_balls_d20a82a9:

    # "Even though she can't just come out and make her intentions clear, they may be good intentions after all, and I think I'm starting to like her more."
    "静音は言葉を発して気持ちをはっきり伝えることはできないけど、どちらにしてもその気持ちは善意のものなのかもしれない。俺は静音を好きになり始めてるな、と思う。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3785
translate jp a1_sunday_throwing_balls_7a69c090:

    # hi "I could skip going, but it'd be a waste. And I want to go, too. I mean, you know, today does seem pretty exciting. If anything, it'll be interesting."
    hi "すっぽかすこともできるけど、そんなのもったいないだろ。それに俺だって行きたいんだ。なんだ、ほら、今日ってかなり楽しそうじゃん。行けば面白いことになりそうだし"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3792
translate jp a1_sunday_throwing_balls_1663aa36:

    # ke "The Student Council? What? That's still around?"
    ke "生徒会？　はあ？　そんなのまだ存在してたのか"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3794
translate jp a1_sunday_throwing_balls_8fdee542:

    # ke "Isn't it like, two dudes?"
    ke "それってあれだろ、野郎二人だけなんだろ？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3796
translate jp a1_sunday_throwing_balls_5e276d39:

    # hi "They're both girls."
    hi "二人とも女の子だけど"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3803
translate jp a1_sunday_throwing_balls_ff89b76b:

    # ke "Really? Are they cute? Damn, no, wait… are they cute?"
    ke "マジで？　かわいいか？　くそ、そんな、待てよおい……かわいいのか？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3805
translate jp a1_sunday_throwing_balls_b83326f1:

    # ke "No! It doesn't matter! I heard the Student Council president is insane… that whoever it is never talks and only gives orders through flunkies."
    ke "いや！　やっぱりそんなのどうでもいい！　生徒会長は狂ってると聞いたことがある……誰だか知らないけど、絶対に口をきかなくて、いつもパシリを使って命令を伝えるってな"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3810
translate jp a1_sunday_throwing_balls_c82b66ec:

    # ke "Shit, they're the same in every school… Sounds like a cold-hearted bitch. Bitches everywhere."
    ke "ちっ、どの学校でも同じだな……冷血なクソアマか。どこもクソアマだらけだ"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3812
translate jp a1_sunday_throwing_balls_54b261b8:

    # ke "If it's two girls, they outnumber you two-against-one. That is a dangerous situation, dude. Who knows what can happen."
    ke "そいつらが女子二人だとしたら、お前は２対１で数の上では負けてるわけだ。お前、危険な状況だぞ。何が起きるか、わかったもんじゃない"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3814
translate jp a1_sunday_throwing_balls_504bef2d:

    # ke "Damn, the Student Council is just two women, but they hold so much power."
    ke "ちっ、生徒会め、女二人だけなのになんて権力を持ってやがる"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3816
translate jp a1_sunday_throwing_balls_042cb545:

    # ke "They must be stopped."
    ke "奴らを止めないといけない"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3818
translate jp a1_sunday_throwing_balls_7b8716d5:

    # ke "I can see them, plotting ways to push their feminist agenda. I can't trust an administration like that."
    ke "わかるんだ、生徒会はフェミニストの陰謀を推進するべく何かたくらんでる。そんな団体信用できないね"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3820
translate jp a1_sunday_throwing_balls_2835c9ab:

    # ke "This is not cool. Not cool!"
    ke "これはよくない。よくないぞ！"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3825
translate jp a1_sunday_throwing_balls_1273307c:

    # ke "Damn. Shit! Damn!"
    ke "くそ。最悪だ！くそ！"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3831
translate jp a1_sunday_throwing_balls_2419e623:

    # "I ponder what I'd like to do with Shizune and Misha. Deciding it's best to be extra prepared, I duck back into my room to stock my wallet with money."
    "静音とミーシャと何をしようか、と考える。準備は念入りにしておいた方がいいと思い、俺は部屋に戻って財布にお金を補充する。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3836
translate jp a1_sunday_throwing_balls_482fcfb6:

    # "I wonder if they have that game where you try to catch goldfish on a paper net."
    "今日は金魚すくいは出てるのかな。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3838
translate jp a1_sunday_throwing_balls_2b47d300:

    # "It seems way easier than they make it look. Then again, if I were to catch a goldfish, I'd have no real reason to keep it."
    "あれは本当は難しいのに、見た目はずっと簡単そうなんだよな。でも金魚なんてとったところで、別に飼う理由なんてないんだけど。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3840
translate jp a1_sunday_throwing_balls_b67f6f43:

    # "What am I going to do with a fish in my tiny room? Cook it?"
    "こんな小さな部屋で、魚なんて飼ってどうするんだ？　料理して食べるのか？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3842
translate jp a1_sunday_throwing_balls_da0ef315:

    # "I could give it to Shizune, or Misha, but that might be overstepping my bounds."
    "静音かミーシャにあげてもいいけど、それは俺にとっての一線を越えてしまっている気がする。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3844
translate jp a1_sunday_throwing_balls_4de9e970:

    # "It's a real problem. Both of them are cute, but I don't think I have any chance with either of them. Regardless, I mull over the thought of doing it. I imagine how they might react if I were to give them a gift tonight, like a fish or a doll."
    "本当に困ったもんだ。二人ともかわいいけど、どっちも脈があるとは思えない。にもかかわらず、俺は実際にプレゼントした場合のことを考える。 今晩あいつらに何かあげたら、どんな反応をするだろうか、と想像する。金魚とか、ぬいぐるみとか。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3846
translate jp a1_sunday_throwing_balls_c51c6e51:

    # "Misha would probably laugh like she always does. Shizune might slap it out of my hand."
    "ミーシャならたぶんいつもと同じように笑うんだろう。静音は俺の手からはたき落としたりするかもしれない。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3848
translate jp a1_sunday_throwing_balls_1ad3ac0d:

    # "Maybe it isn't such a good idea after all."
    "なんか、やっぱりいい考えじゃないな。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3850
translate jp a1_sunday_throwing_balls_0096ae99:

    # "Okay, I think I'm set."
    "よし、準備オーケーだ。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3854
translate jp a1_sunday_throwing_balls_e7642194:

    # "A good while later, I decide that this could be another psych out test devised by Shizune. Even if it isn't, it's starting to get kind of late."
    "かなり時間が経ってから、これはまた静音が心理戦を仕掛けてきているんじゃないかと思い始める。そうでないとしても、ちょっと遅い時間になっている。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3856
translate jp a1_sunday_throwing_balls_d51603f2:

    # "I resolve to just go out and search for them, even though I don't know where I could look. They might be really hard to find today."
    "ちょっと外に出て二人を探すことにする。とはいえ、どこを探せばいいか見当はついていない。今日あいつらを見つけるのは特に難しそうだ。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3862
translate jp a1_sunday_throwing_balls_a3896399:

    # "As soon as I step outside, I almost bump into Shizune."
    "外に一歩出たとたん、静音にぶつかりそうになる。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3864
translate jp a1_sunday_throwing_balls_1cf2c14f:

    # hi "Hi, Shizune. Where's Misha?"
    hi "よう、静音。ミーシャはどこだ？"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3869
translate jp a1_sunday_throwing_balls_e45805b3:

    # "I try to sign it as best as I can, but really I'm just making stuff up. I've got to ask Misha to teach me some of this."
    "どうにかして手話で伝えようとするけど、実際はただのでたらめだ。ミーシャに少しやり方を教わらないとだめだな。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3871
translate jp a1_sunday_throwing_balls_02f7fa71:

    # mi "Here!"
    mi "ここだよ！"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3882
translate jp a1_sunday_throwing_balls_89594031:

    # "Misha pops up from behind Shizune, grinning widely."
    "にこにこと笑いながら、ミーシャが静音の後ろから飛び出す。"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3887
translate jp a1_sunday_throwing_balls_a10b8ec0:

    # mi "We just came to make sure you're coming along with us to the festival."
    mi "ちゃんとひっちゃんが一緒に学園祭に来てくれるか、確かめに来たんだよ"

# game/script-a1-sunday.rpy:3892
